《權力遊戲》第一季的[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2010年7月26日開始<ref name="gotfactsheet" />，而主要位置是在[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[貝爾法斯特|貝爾法斯特]]的{{le|Paint Hall工作室|Northern Ireland Screen}}<ref name="nigov">{{cite press release | title = HBO to film TV pilot in Belfast, Northern Ireland | publisher = Northern Ireland Executive | date = 2009-04-21 | url = http://www.northernireland.gov.uk/news/news-ofmdfm/news-ofmdfm-210409-hbo-to-film.htm | access-date = 2011-06-20 | archive-date = 2016-04-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160430032117/http://www.northernireland.gov.uk/news/news-ofmdfm/news-ofmdfm-210409-hbo-to-film.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。北愛爾蘭的外景是在[[蒙恩山脈|蒙恩山脈]]的桑迪布雷（Sandy Brae）、{{le|Ward城堡|Castle Ward}}<ref name="castlewardmb">{{cite web | url=http://theministerspen.blogspot.com/2009/11/game-of-thrones.html | title=Game of Thrones | last=McCausland | first=Nelson | date=2009-11-05 | work=Nelson's View – The Minister's Pen | publisher=Blogger | accessdate=2011-06-20 | archive-date=2016-08-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817123724/http://theministerspen.blogspot.com/2009/11/game-of-thrones.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>、聖菲爾德莊園、{{le|塔利莫爾森林公園|Tollymore Forest Park}}<ref name="shanecastlebbc" />、{{le|塚堡|Carncastle}}及{{le|沙恩城堡|Shane's Castle}}拍攝<ref name="USA Today March 30, 2012">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401123724/http://travel.usatoday.com/destinations/story/2012-04-01/Where-the-HBO-hit-Game-of-Thrones-was-filmed/53876876/1 |archivedate=2012-04-01 |url=http://travel.usatoday.com/destinations/story/2012-04-01/Where-the-HBO-hit-Game-of-Thrones-was-filmed/53876876/1 |title=Where HBO's hit 'Game of Thrones' was filmed |work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |first=Josh |last=Roberts |date=2012-04-01 |accessdate=2013-03-08}}</ref><ref name="shanecastlebbc">{{Cite video | people = Maggie Taggart | title = Fantasy epic to be filmed in Belfast | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/8548527.stm | publisher = BBC News | location = Belfast | date = 2010-03-03 | access-date = 2011-06-20 | archive-date = 2016-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160811141708/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/8548527.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Published on Thu Jun 24 13:40:52 BST 2010 |url=http://www.larnetimes.co.uk/news/Extras-needed-for-new-TV.6382643.jp |title=Extras needed for new TV show – Local |publisher=Larne Times |date= |accessdate=2011-05-11 }}{{Dead link|date=2020年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[史特靈|斯特靈]]的{{le|杜恩城堡|Doune Castle}}也用於溫特費爾場景的原版試播情節<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811101337/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/scotland/tayside_and_central/8322843.stm |archivedate=2016-08-11 |title=Medieval keep becomes film set |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/scotland/tayside_and_central/8322843.stm |accessdate=2012-04-11 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2009-10-23 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbcnewsdoune">{{cite press release | title = Medieval keep becomes film set | publisher = BBC News | date = 2009-10-23 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/scotland/tayside_and_central/8322843.stm | access-date = 2011-06-20 | archive-date = 2016-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160811101337/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/scotland/tayside_and_central/8322843.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。製片人最初考慮整個系列都在蘇格蘭拍攝，但由於工作室空間有限，故決定選擇北愛爾蘭<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529084634/http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/scotland-mourning-the-loss-of-epic-160m-tv-opportunity.21352049 |archivedate=2015-05-29 |last=Miller |first=Phil |title=Beaten in Game of Thrones: why Scotland lost £160m chance to host TV series |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/scotland-mourning-the-loss-of-epic-160m-tv-opportunity.21352049 |accessdate=2013-06-17 |newspaper=[[The_Herald_(Glasgow)|The Herald]] |date=2013-06-17 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第一季的南部場景是在[[馬耳他|馬耳他]]拍攝的，試播劇集的摩洛哥設定於地點發生了變化<ref name="gotfactsheet"/>。[[姆迪納|姆迪納]]的城市被用作國王的登陸地<ref name="gotfactsheet" />。在2009年最初的試拍時<ref name="ctryanbran">{{cite news | last =Ryan | first =Maureen | title =The 'Games' afoot: HBO's 'Game of Thrones' gears up | date =2009-10-13 | url =http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2009/10/game-of-thrones-hbo.html | accessdate =2009-01-13 | work =Chicago Tribune | archive-date =2016-08-17 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160817123724/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2009/10/game-of-thrones-hbo.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>，劇組也考慮在{{le|馬諾埃爾堡|Fort Manoel}}、[[馬耳他|馬耳他]][[戈佐岛|哥佐島]]的[[藍窗|藍窗]]、以及{{le|聖安東宮|San Anton Palace}}、{{le|里卡索利堡|Fort Ricasoli}}、{{le|聖安吉洛堡|Fort St. Angelo}}，和聖多米尼克修道院（St. Dominic monastery）拍攝<ref name="USA Today March 30, 2012" />。

[[File:Dubrovnik_crop.jpg|thumb]]的[[城牆|城牆]]在第2季中成為了君臨城。]]
第二季的南部拍攝場景從馬耳他轉到克羅地亞，[[杜布羅夫尼克|杜布羅夫尼克]]市及鄰近地點，容許對這座有圍牆的沿海中世紀城市進行外部拍攝。[[杜布羅夫尼克城牆|杜布羅夫尼克城牆]]和[[羅維里耶納克要塞|羅維里耶納克要塞]]被用作拍攝君臨城的場景，但是一些當地建築物的外觀，例如紅堡（Red Keep）和貝勒大聖堂（Sept of Baelor），都是由電腦合成的<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-stunning-visual-effects-reel-separates-the-real-from-the-fake-in-season-five-10393725.html/ |title=Game of Thrones: Stunning visual effects reel separates the real from the fake in season five |work=The Independent |first=Jess |last=Denham |date=2015-07-16 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519213501/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-stunning-visual-effects-reel-separates-the-real-from-the-fake-in-season-five-10393725.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[洛克魯姆島|洛克魯姆島]]，在[[特羅吉爾|特羅吉爾]]沿海城市的聖多米尼克修道院，[[總督宮_(杜布羅夫尼克)|杜布羅夫尼克總督宮]]，及杜巴克採石場（向東幾公里）都用作魁爾斯（Qarth）的場景。2011年11月，劇組於冰島拍攝弗羅斯特芳斯（Frostfangs）和在第一個人拳頭的隔離牆以北場景，那是位於鄰近斯米爾拉柏格（Smyrlabjörg）的[[瓦特納冰原|瓦特納冰原]]，鄰近{{le|斯卡夫塔費德|Skaftafell}}的斯維納（Svínafellsjökull）冰川，以及鄰近[[維克_(冰島)|冰島維克]]的[[米達爾斯冰原|米達爾斯冰原]]冰川<ref name="USA Today March 30, 2012" /><ref name="location iceland">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826083416/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/iceland/articles/game-of-thrones-iceland-tour-filming-locations/ |archivedate=2016-08-26 |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/destinations/europe/iceland/articles/game-of-thrones-iceland-tour-filming-locations/ |title=Iceland's most spectacular Game of Thrones filming locations |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |first=Oliver |last=Smith |date=2016-06-07 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

