第三季的製作又回到了杜布羅夫尼克、杜布羅夫尼克城牆、洛夫里耶納克堡，以及用於拍攝君臨城和紅堡的附近地點。新的拍攝地點—{{le|特雷斯蒂諾樹木園|Trsteno Arboretum}}，是君臨城裡泰瑞爾的花園。第三季也回到摩洛哥（包括[[索維拉|索維拉]]的城市）來拍攝在埃索斯（Essos）中丹妮莉絲（Daenerys）的場景<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617031757/http://www.salon.com/2014/04/29/the_7_kingdoms_in_game_of_thrones_are_actually_these_5_real_world_places_partner/ |archivedate=2016-06-17 |url=http://www.salon.com/2014/04/29/the_7_kingdoms_in_game_of_thrones_are_actually_these_5_real_world_places_partner/ |title=The 7 kingdoms in 'Game of Thrones' are actually these 5 real-world places |work=[[Salon_(website)|Salon]] |first=Jessica |last=Phelan |date=2014-04-29 |accessdate=2014-08-23 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|黑暗城堡熔岩群|Dimmuborgir}}和{{le|冰島米湖|Grjótagjá}}的洞穴也有被使用<ref name="location iceland"/>。有一個與{{le|真熊|Bart the Bear 2}}拍攝的場景於[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]進行<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016062544/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2013/01/game-of-thrones-casts-a-bear-and-shoots-in-los-angeles-for-major-season-3-scene.html |archivedate=2013-10-16 |title='Game of Thrones' casts a bear and shoots in Los Angeles for major Season 3 scene |last=Schwartz |first=Terri |date=2013-01-28 |publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]] |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2013/01/game-of-thrones-casts-a-bear-and-shoots-in-los-angeles-for-major-season-3-scene.html |accessdate=2013-03-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。製作方面使用了三個單位（龍、狼和渡鴉）並行拍攝，過程涉及六個導演小組、257位演員和703個劇組人員<ref name="Making">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130306120407/http://www.makinggameofthrones.com/production-diary/2012/11/2/season-3-by-the-numbers.html |archivedate=2013-03-06 |title=Season 3: by the Numbers |url=http://www.makinggameofthrones.com/production-diary/2012/11/2/season-3-by-the-numbers.htm |website=Making Game of Thrones |accessdate=2012-11-03 |date=2012-11-02}}</ref>。

第四季的製作又回到杜布羅夫尼克，其中包括一些新地點，包括[[斯普利特|施普利特]]的[[戴克里先宮|戴克里先宮]]、北邊的[[克利斯要塞|克利斯要塞]]、東邊的秘魯採石場，{{le|摩索山脈|Mosor}}和再往南走的[[巴什卡沃達|巴什卡沃達]]<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224065003/http://winteriscoming.net/2013/09/new-set-photos-from-klis-and-dubrovnik/ |archivedate=2013-12-24 |url=http://winteriscoming.net/2013/09/new-set-photos-from-klis-and-dubrovnik/ |title=New set photos from Klis and Dubrovnik |publisher=WinterIsComing.net |date=2013-09-18 |accessdate=2013-09-19 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。冰島的[[辛格韋德利|辛格維勒國家公園]]曾被用作拍攝布蕾妮與獵犬之間的鬥爭<ref name="location iceland"/>。拍攝為期136天，並於2013年11月21日結束<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222200023/http://winteriscoming.net/2013/11/thats-a-wrap-season-4-filming-is-complete/ |archivedate=2014-02-22 |url=http://winteriscoming.net/2013/11/thats-a-wrap-season-4-filming-is-complete/ |title=That's a wrap! Season 4 filming is complete |publisher=WinterIsComing.net |date=2013-11-21 |accessdate=2013-11-26 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。第五季新增了[[西班牙|西班牙]][[塞维利亚|西維爾]]，還有[[哥多華_(西班牙)|西班牙的哥多華]]，用於[[冰與火之歌的世界#多恩|多恩]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103546/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/jul/06/game-of-thrones-fifth-series-10000-spaniards-extras-spain |archivedate=2016-03-04 |last=Burgen |first=Stephen |title=Game of Thrones fifth series: more than 10,000 Spaniards apply to be extras |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/jul/06/game-of-thrones-fifth-series-10000-spaniards-extras-spain |date=2014-07-06 |accessdate=2014-07-26 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

至於第六季，拍攝始於2015年7月，並回到西班牙，在[[納瓦拉|納瓦拉]]、[[瓜達拉哈拉省|瓜達拉哈拉省]]、[[塞维利亚|西維爾]]、[[阿尔梅里亚|阿爾梅里亞]]、[[赫罗纳|基羅納]]和[[佩尼伊斯科拉|佩尼伊斯科拉]]<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530024956/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/06/02/game-thrones-spain |archivedate=2016-05-30 |url=https://ew.com/article/2015/06/02/game-thrones-spain |title=''Game of Thrones'' returning to Spain for season 6 |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=2015-06-03 |accessdate=2015-06-03 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。拍攝也回到克羅地亞的杜布羅夫尼克<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/611134/Game-of-Thrones-season-6-Lena-Headey-HBO-Cersei-Lannister-Croatia-Dubrovnik |title=Game of Thrones season 6: Lena Headey spotted filming in Croatia |work=Daily Express |first=Neela |last=Debnath |date=2015-10-09 |accessdate=2017-07-17 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716061155/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequels-are-we-getting-all-four-1020065 |archivedate=2017-07-16 }}</ref>。第七季的七集於2016年8月31日開始拍攝，劇組於貝爾法斯特的鐵達尼工作室（Titanic Studios）進行拍攝，以及在冰島、北愛爾蘭和西班牙許多地方進行其他的拍攝<ref>{{cite news |last=Smith |first=Oliver |date=2016-09-23 |title=The incredible locations that will star in Game of Thrones season 7 |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/arts-and-culture/filming-locations-game-of-thrones-season-seven/ |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |location=London |access-date=2017-01-01 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102082411/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/arts-and-culture/filming-locations-game-of-thrones-season-seven/ |archivedate=2017-01-02 }}</ref>，包括[[塞维利亚|西維爾]]、[[卡塞雷斯_(西班牙)|西班牙卡塞雷斯]]、[[阿爾莫多瓦-德爾里奧|阿爾莫多瓦-德爾里奧]]、[[桑蒂蓬塞|桑蒂蓬塞]]、[[蘇馬亞|蘇馬亞]]和[[貝爾梅奧|貝爾梅奧]]<ref>{{cite press |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/https://medium.com/hbo-cinemax-pr/game-of-thrones-s7-production-9c12d317565d |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://medium.com/hbo-cinemax-pr/game-of-thrones-s7-production-9c12d317565d |title=EMMY®- AND GOLDEN GLOBE-WINNING HBO SERIES GAME OF THRONES TO BEGIN PRODUCTION ON SEASON SEVEN THIS SUMMER |publisher=[[HBO|HBO]] |date=2016-07-18 |accessdate=2016-08-31 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。該系列還在杜布羅夫尼克拍攝，用於描述君臨城的其他地方<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thedubrovniktimes.com/news/dubrovnik/item/1631-photo-video-exclusive-game-of-thrones-is-back-in-dubrovnik |title=EXCLUSIVE – Game of Thrones is back in Dubrovnik |work=The Dubrovnik Times |date=2016-12-14 |accessdate=2017-07-17 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702082729/http://thedubrovniktimes.com/news/dubrovnik/item/1631-photo-video-exclusive-game-of-thrones-is-back-in-dubrovnik |archivedate=2017-07-02 }}</ref>。為確保某些歐洲地區的冬季天氣而必需拍攝持續到2017年2月底<ref>{{cite news |url=http://tvline.com/2016/07/06/game-of-thrones-season-7-premiere-date-delayed-new-interview/ |title=''Game of Thrones'' Season 7 Production Delayed |work=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |first=Andy |last=Swift |accessdate=2016-07-06 |date=2016-07-06 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160707215822/http://tvline.com/2016/07/06/game-of-thrones-season-7-premiere-date-delayed-new-interview/ |archivedate=2016-07-07 }}</ref>。

==== 地點的影響 ====
《權力遊戲》是由{{le|北愛爾蘭屏幕|Northern Ireland Screen}}資助，那是由{{le|北愛爾蘭投資|Invest Northern Ireland}}及{{le|歐洲區域發展基金|European Regional Development Fund}}資助的英國政府機構<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://northernirelandscreen.co.uk/news/2919/game-of-thrones-season-3-to-film-in-northern-ireland.aspx |archivedate=2016-08-21 |publisher=Northern Ireland Screen |title=Game of Thrones season 3 to film in Northern Ireland |url=http://northernirelandscreen.co.uk/news/2919/game-of-thrones-season-3-to-film-in-northern-ireland.aspx |accessdate=2012-04-12 |date=2012-04-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。{{as of|2013|April}}，北愛爾蘭投資為該系列提供了£925萬英鎊（約$1,437萬美元）；據政府估計，這為[[北愛爾蘭經濟|北愛爾蘭經濟]]帶來了£6,500萬英鎊（約$1.0095億美元）的收益<ref name="bradley20120412" />。

{{le|愛爾蘭旅遊局|Tourism Ireland}}以《權力遊戲》為主題的營銷活動，這類似於新西蘭{{le|跟托爾金相關的廣告|Tolkien tourism}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tourismireland.com/Press-Releases/2016/April/New-advertising-campaign-to-showcase-Northern-Irel |title=New advertising campaign to showcase Northern Ireland to millions of Game of Thrones® fans worldwide |publisher=Tourism Ireland |date=2016-04-26 |accessdate=2017-06-17 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819054509/https://www.tourismireland.com/Press-Releases/2016/April/New-advertising-campaign-to-showcase-Northern-Irel |archivedate=2017-08-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.businessworld.ie/news/Tourism-Ireland-wins-top-marketing-award-for-Game-of-Thrones-campaign-562193.html |title=Tourism Ireland wins top marketing award for Game of Thrones campaign |publisher=Business World |first=Robert |last=McHugh |date=2015-12-14 |accessdate=2017-06-17 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819054510/https://www.businessworld.ie/news/Tourism-Ireland-wins-top-marketing-award-for-Game-of-Thrones-campaign-562193.html |archivedate=2017-08-19 }}</ref><!-- The reference to Tolkien tourism comes from the previously cited source @ https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://qz.com/196010/will-game-of-thrones-make-ireland-the-next-new-zealand/ -->。北愛爾蘭投資與{{le|北愛爾蘭旅遊局|Northern Ireland Tourist Board}}也希望該系列能夠產生旅遊收益<ref name=bradley20120412>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508092252/http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/media/the-game-of-thrones-tourists-1.1357475 |archivedate=2013-05-08 |last=Bradley |first=Una |title=The 'Game of Thrones' tourists: How much is the hit HBO fantasy series worth to its home, Northern Ireland? |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/media/the-game-of-thrones-tourists-1.1357475 |accessdate=2013-04-12 |newspaper=[[The_Irish_Times|The Irish Times]] |date=2013-04-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[范愛玲|范愛玲]]的說法，該系列劇集為北愛爾蘭提供了有史以來最[[北愛爾蘭問題|非政治性]]的宣傳<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/news/game-of-thrones-pumped-43m-into-northern-irelands-economy-and-more-could-be-on-the-way-28749710.html |title=Game of Thrones pumped £43m into Northern Ireland's economy, and more could be on the way |work=[[The_Belfast_Telegraph|The Belfast Telegraph]] |date=2012-05-16 |accessdate=2012-05-16 |last = McAdam |first = Noel |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716061155/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequels-are-we-getting-all-four-1020065 |archivedate=2017-07-16 }}</ref>。《權力遊戲》和其他電視連續劇的製作也促進了北愛爾蘭的創意產業的發展，在2008年至2013年之間它們為藝術，娛樂和休閒工作估計貢獻了12.4％的增長（相比同期英國其他地區的4.3％）<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-27360311 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Pym |first=Hugh |title=Game of Thrones boost to economy in Northern Ireland |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-27360311 |accessdate=2014-05-11 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2014-05-11 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年9月，HBO宣布計劃將拍攝結束後的北愛爾蘭的地區，於2019年開放成為旅遊景點<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/game-of-thrones-tourist-attractions-northern-ireland-1202954302/ |title='Game of Thrones' Filming Locations in Northern Ireland to Open as Tourist Attractions |first=Todd |last=Spangler |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2018-09-24 |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2019-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929021705/https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/game-of-thrones-tourist-attractions-northern-ireland-1202954302/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

其他地區的旅遊組織報告指，他們的地點出現於《權力遊戲》後，預訂量增加了。2012年，杜布羅夫尼克於{{le|LateRooms.com|LateRooms.com}}上的預訂增加了28％，而冰島增加了13％。翌年，摩洛哥[[瓦爾扎扎特|瓦爾扎扎特]]的預訂量增長了一倍（第三季丹妮莉絲的演出地點）<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.femalefirst.co.uk/travel/game-of-thrones-filming-locations-288707.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Adam |first=Shabana |title=Travel News: Game of Thrones Sparks Big Boosts in Hotel Bookings to Filming Locations |url=http://www.femalefirst.co.uk/travel/game-of-thrones-filming-locations-288707.html |accessdate=2013-04-18 |publisher=Female First |date=2013-04-17}}</ref>。《權力遊戲》被認為是冰島旅遊業蓬勃發展的重要因素，對冰島的經濟產生了重大影響。2015年，遊客人數增加了30％，2016年又增加了40％<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-05-03/world-beating-krona-weathers-iceland-s-rate-cuts-on-tourism-boom |title=Game of Thrones Crowns Iceland Krona as World's Best Currency |first=Love |last=Liman |date=2017-05-03 |work=Bloomberg |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504043446/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-05-03/world-beating-krona-weathers-iceland-s-rate-cuts-on-tourism-boom |archivedate=2017-05-04 }}</ref>，預計到2016年最終人數將達到240萬人次，佔該國人口的7倍左右<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newsweek.com/iceland-game-thrones-hbo-westeros-krona-593949 |title=Iceland's Economy is Booming—Thanks to a Little Help from Game of Throne |first=Josh |last=Lowe |date=2017-05-03 |work=Newsweek |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504233103/http://www.newsweek.com/iceland-game-thrones-hbo-westeros-krona-593949 |archivedate=2017-05-04 }}</ref>。然而，杜布羅夫尼克旅遊業的增長，估計《權力遊戲》佔其多年來多年年均增長的一半，導致人們對「過度旅遊」的擔憂，使其市長限制該市的遊客人數<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thedubrovniktimes.com/lifestyle/feature/item/2945-game-changer-how-dubrovnik-benefits-and-loses-from-being-king-s-landing |title=Game Changer: How Dubrovnik Benefits and Loses from Being King's Landing |author=Mirella-Marie Katarina Radman |date=2017-08-20 |work=The Dubrovnik Times |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2019-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709162748/https://www.thedubrovniktimes.com/lifestyle/feature/item/2945-game-changer-how-dubrovnik-benefits-and-loses-from-being-king-s-landing |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/19/world/europe/dubrovnik-croatia-game-of-thrones.html |title=Throngs Enticed by 'Game of Thrones' Threaten a Magical City |date=2018-08-19 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2020-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829092251/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/19/world/europe/dubrovnik-croatia-game-of-thrones.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 執導 ===
《權力遊戲》的幾個季度裡包括了４至６名導演，他們通常都以背對背的形式拍攝。[[亞倫·泰勒_(導演)|阿倫·泰勒]]執導了７集，是該系列中最多的一個。{{le|阿歷克斯·格雷夫斯|Alex Graves}}、[[戴維·納特|戴維·納特]]、{{le|馬克·邁洛德|Mark Mylod}}和{{le|傑里米·波德斯瓦|Jeremy Podeswa}}分別執導了六集；{{le|丹尼爾·米納漢|Daniel Minahan}}執導了五集；而[[蜜雪兒·麥勞倫|蜜雪兒·麥勞倫]]、{{le|阿里克·薩哈羅夫|Alik Sakharov}}及{{le|米格爾·薩波奇尼克|Miguel Sapochnik}}每人執導了四集，而麥勞倫還是整個系列中唯一的女性導演<ref>{{cite news|last=Moreau|first=Jordan|title=Jessica Chastain, Ava DuVernay Call Out ‘Game of Thrones’ for Treatment of Women|url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/jessica-chastain-ava-duvernay-game-of-thrones-women-1203207692/|accessdate=2019-05-21|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Variety Media, LLC|date=2019-05-07|archive-date=2020-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512195149/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/jessica-chastain-ava-duvernay-game-of-thrones-women-1203207692/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|布萊恩·柯克|Brian Kirk}}在第一季中執導了三集，而[[提姆·范恩·派頓|提姆·范恩·派頓]]執導了該劇集的前兩集。[[尼爾·馬歇爾|尼爾·馬歇爾]]執導了兩集，均帶有大型的戰鬥場面：「{{le|黑水之戰|Blackwater (Game of Thrones)}}」和「{{le|城牆上的看守者|The Watchers on the Wall}}」。其他的導演有：[[傑克·本德|傑克·本德]]、{{le|大衛·彼得拉卡|David Petrarca}}、{{le|丹尼爾·薩克海姆|Daniel Sackheim}}、{{le|米高·斯洛維斯|Michael Slovis}}和{{le|馬特·沙克曼|Matt Shakman}}<ref name="Directors">{{cite web |url=https://gamesradar.com/game-of-thrones-season-7/ |title=Game of Thrones season 7: US and UK air date, teaser trailer, official poster, cast, rumors, and everything you need to know |work=GamesRadar |accessdate=2017-04-04 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404215853/http://www.gamesradar.com/game-of-thrones-season-7/ |archivedate=2017-04-04 }}</ref>。貝尼奧夫和魏斯一起執導了兩集，但每集只記了一個名稱，並由擲銀後決定的<ref name="hbo cast"/><ref name="vanity fair"/>。

=== 技術方面 ===
{{le|阿里克·薩哈羅夫|Alik Sakharov}}是試播時的攝影師。該系列有許多攝影師<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cinematographers.nl/PaginasDoPh/sakharov.htm |title=ALIK SAKHAROV ASC |publisher=Cinematographers |accessdate=2016-08-29 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170125162551/http://www.cinematographers.nl/PaginasDoPh/sakharov.htm |archivedate=2017-01-25 }}</ref>，並獲得７項{{le|黃金時段艾美獎單攝影機系列傑出攝影獎（一小時）|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Cinematography for a Single-Camera Series (One Hour)}}的提名<ref name="emmys.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.emmys.com/shows/game-thrones |title=Game of Thrones |publisher=[[Emmy_Award|Emmys.com]] |accessdate=2016-02-21 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170413192605/http://www.emmys.com/shows/game-thrones |archivedate=2017-04-13 }}</ref>。奧諾·諾里·奧特（Oral Norrey Ottey）、弗朗西斯·帕克（Frances Parker）、馬丁·尼科爾臣（Martin Nicholson）、克里斯平·格林（Crispin Green）、{{le|添·波特|Tim Porter}}和凱蒂·韋蘭德（Katie Weiland）已編輯了該系列的不同集數。韋蘭德於2015年獲得《[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]》的{{le|黃金時段艾美獎戲劇系列單機攝影出色獎|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Single-Camera Picture Editing for a Drama Series}}<ref name="emmys.com"/>。

=== 製作設計 ===
==== 服裝 ====
