{{le|米歇爾·克萊普頓|Michele Clapton}}是《權力遊戲》首五季的[[劇裝設計|劇裝設計]]師，隨後她由{{le|愛普·費利|April Ferry}}取代<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-costume-designer-april-803895 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-costume-designer-april-803895 |title='Game of Thrones' Season 6 Adds New Costume Designer |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |first=Merle |last=Ginsberg |date=2015-06-19 |accessdate=2015-12-13 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。克萊普頓以第七季服裝設計師的身份重返系列的崗位<ref name="www.ew.com game-thrones-season-7">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/29/game-thrones-season-7 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://ew.com/article/2016/06/29/game-thrones-season-7 |title=Game of Thrones season 7 directors revealed |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |last=Hibberd |first=James |date=2016-06-29 |accessdate=2016-06-29 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該系列中使用的服裝從從許多來源中汲取靈感，例如日本盔甲及波斯盔甲。多斯拉克禮服類似於[[貝都因人|貝都因人]]的服裝（其中一個是用魚皮製成的，類似於龍鱗），而野人就如[[因纽特人|因纽特人]]那樣穿著動物皮毛<ref name="wischhover20120604">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20120606175316/http://fashionista.com/2012/06/game-of-thrones-hair-and-wardrobe-secrets-revealed/ |archivedate=2012-06-06 |url=http://fashionista.com/2012/06/game-of-thrones-hair-and-wardrobe-secrets-revealed/ |title=Game of Thrones' Hair and Wardrobe Secrets Revealed |work=Fashionista |date=2012-06-04 |accessdate=2012-06-06 |last = Wischhover |first = Cheryl |dead-url=no}}</ref>。野人的骨頭裝甲由實際骨骼的模具製成，並使用類似於[[羊腸線|羊腸線]]的線和乳膠組裝而成<ref name="Snead, Elizabeth">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/fash-track/game-thrones-michelle-clapton-costume-designer-emmy-335607 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/fash-track/game-thrones-michelle-clapton-costume-designer-emmy-335607 |title='Game of Thrones' Designer Michelle Clapton's Secret Source for Wildling Bones: eBay |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2012-06-11 |accessdate=2012-06-11 |last = Snead |first = Elizabeth |dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管飾演「野人」和「守夜人」的演員通常戴著帽子（正常在寒冷的天氣下），主角成員通常不會這樣做，因此觀眾可以識別主角人物。[[碧玉_(歌手)|碧玉]]的[[亞歷山大·麥昆|亞歷山大·麥昆]]高領裙受到{{le|瑪格麗·泰瑞爾|Margaery Tyrell}}的漏斗領服裝的啟發，而娼妓的服裝為易於除脫而設計<ref name="wischhover20120604" />。所有使用過的衣服都使用了兩個星期，因此在高清電視上看起來很現實<ref name="Snead, Elizabeth"/>。

眾女演員使用了大約兩打假髮。那些假髮由人類頭髮製成，長度達{{convert|2|ft|cm|disp=flip}}，每個假髮的價格都高達$7,000美元，並能夠如真髮一樣被清洗和造型。然而戴假髮是很費時的事，就如[[艾美莉·克拉克|艾美莉·克拉克]]，大約需要兩個小時才能把她的深褐色頭髮造型至淡金黃色假髮配上辮子。而其他演員，例如[[傑克·格利森|傑克·格利森]]和[[蘇菲·特納|蘇菲·特納]]，他們都需要經常[[染髮|染髮]]。對於像丹妮莉絲（克拉克）和她的多瑟基（Dothraki）等的角色，他們的頭髮、假髮和服飾都經過加工，使它看起來好像有好幾個星期已沒有洗過了<ref name="wischhover20120604"/>。

==== 化妝 ====
在首三個季度中，{{le|保羅·恩格倫|Paul Engelen}}是《權力遊戲》的主要化妝設計師和修復化妝師，其他的化妝師梅利莎·拉克斯汀（Melissa Lackersteen）、{{le|科納·奧沙利文|Conor O'Sullivan (make-up artist)}}及羅布·特倫頓（Rob Trenton）。在第四季開始，恩格倫的團隊由珍·沃克及其團隊取代，該團隊由安·麥伊恩（Ann McEwan）及巴利（Barrie）和莎拉·高爾（Sarah Gower）組成<ref name="emmys.com"/><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.westeros.org/GoT/News/Entry/Game_of_Thrones_Wins_Big_at_Creative_Arts_Emmys/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=http://www.westeros.org/GoT/News/Entry/Game_of_Thrones_Wins_Big_at_Creative_Arts_Emmys/ |title=Game of Thrones Wins Big at Creative Arts Emmys |work=Westeros.org |date=2012-09-16 |accessdate=2016-02-21 |author=Elio |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 視覺特效 ===
《權力遊戲》系列中有大量的[[視覺效果|視覺效果]]。HBO在第一季聘請了英國的BlueBolt和愛爾蘭的Screen Scene來製作。大多數環境構建都是以[[偽三維|2.5D]]投影來完成的，讓觀眾獲得透視圖之餘，同時又可以防止編程過於繁瑣<ref name=vfx-got>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514050245/http://www.westeros.org/GoT/Features/Entry/Interview_with_VFX_Producer_Lucy_Ainsworth-Taylor/|archivedate=2016-05-14|last=Elio|title=Interview with VFX Producer Lucy Ainsworth-Taylor|url=http://www.westeros.org/GoT/Features/Entry/Interview_with_VFX_Producer_Lucy_Ainsworth-Taylor/|publisher=Westeros.org|date=2011-06-22|accessdate=2014-08-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，第一季的結局《{{le|火與血|Fire and Blood (Game of Thrones)}}》，獲提名到[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]的「{{le|傑出視覺特效|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Special Visual Effects}}」<ref name="emmys.com"/>。

由於在隨後季度的特效變得更加複雜（包括[[電腦圖形|電腦圖像]]的生物，火焰和水），來自德國的{{le|Pixomondo|Pixomondo}}成為了視覺效果的主要製作人；其12個工場中的9個都為第二季作出貢獻，其中以[[斯图加特|史特加]]為首<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718224036/http://www.pixomondo.com/portfolio/game-of-thrones/ |archivedate=2016-07-18 |title=Game of Thrones: Season 2 |url=http://www.pixomondo.com/portfolio/game-of-thrones/ |publisher=[[Pixomondo|Pixomondo]] |accessdate=2014-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.pixomondo.com/portfolio/game-of-thrones-season-3/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |title=Game of Thrones: Season 3 |url=http://www.pixomondo.com/portfolio/game-of-thrones-season-3/ |publisher=Pixomondo |accessdate=2014-08-19 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。場景也由英國的Peanut FX、加拿大的Spin VFX，以及美國的Gradient Effects製作。{{le|瓦拉爾莫古利斯|Valar Morghulis}}和{{le|瓦拉爾多哈里斯|Valar Dohaeris}}分別在2012年和2013年獲得Pixomondo黃金時段艾美獎最佳特殊視覺效果獎<ref name="emmys.com"/>。

在第四個季度，HBO把德國的Mackevision加入到項目中<ref name=mckvsn>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821120407/http://mackevision.com/123live-user-data/user_data/6084/public/DOWNLOADS_DE/HOME/20140710_GOT_Nominierung_de.pdf |archivedate=2014-08-21 |title=Mackevision erhält Emmy-Nominierung für visuelle Effekte in "Game of Thrones" – Pressemeldung |url=http://mackevision.com/123live-user-data/user_data/6084/public/DOWNLOADS_DE/HOME/20140710_GOT_Nominierung_de.pdf |publisher=Mackevision |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-08-19 |language=de }}</ref>。到第四季結局《{{le|兒童|The Children (Game of Thrones)}}》榮獲2014年艾美獎的「視覺效果獎」。第四季的其他製作人包括加拿大的{{le|Rodeo FX|Rodeo FX}}，德國的{{le|Scanline VFX|Scanline VFX}}和美國的BAKED FX。在第四季和第五季中，青春期龍的肌肉和翅膀運動主要是基於雞隻。Pixomondo保留了一個由22至30個人組成的團隊，專門研究可視化丹妮莉絲·坦格利安的龍，平均每季的製作時間為20—22個星期<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/innovations/Game-of-thrones-dragons |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Johnson |first=Thomas |title=How 'Game of Thrones' creates its dragons |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/innovations/Game-of-thrones-dragons |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |accessdate=2015-04-12 |date=2015-03-19}}</ref>。在第五季，HBO將美國的瘋馬特效（Crazy Horse Effects）及加拿大的{{le|圖像引擎|Image Engine}}納入了主要視覺效果製作者名單<ref>{{cite web |url=http://image-engine.com/tv/game-of-thrones/ |title=Game of Thrones |publisher=Image Engine |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716061155/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequels-are-we-getting-all-four-1020065 |archivedate=2017-07-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chevfx.com/current-projects.php |title=Current Projects |publisher=Crazy Horse Effects |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601231708/http://www.chevfx.com/current-projects.php |archivedate=2015-06-01 }}</ref>。

==== 片頭 ====
該系列的片頭是由製作工作室Elastic為HBO創建的。[[創意總監|創意總監]]{{le|安格斯·沃爾|Angus Wall}}及他的合作者獲得了2011年[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]的「主要標題設計獎」<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emmys-2011-game-thrones-title-233780 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Fernandez |first=Sofia M. |title=Emmys 2011: 'Game of Thrones' Title Sequence Gives Series Its First Emmy |url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/news/emmys-2011-game-thrones-title-233780 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |newspaper=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2011-09-10 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中他們描繪了[[冰與火之歌的世界|該系列的虛構世界]]的三維地圖。該地圖投影在一個球體的內部，它在[[環形球儀|環形球儀]]被小太陽集中照射<ref name="Art of the Title 2013">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.artofthetitle.com/title/game-of-thrones/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Perkins |first=Will |title=Game of Thrones (2011) |url=http://www.artofthetitle.com/title/game-of-thrones/ |accessdate=2013-06-01 |publisher=Art of the Title |date=2011-05-11 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。當相機在地圖上移動時，它專注於劇集事件發生的位置，發條機制交織並允許建築物和其他結構從地圖上浮現出來。伴隨著{{le|權力遊戲主題音樂|Music of Game of Thrones}}，主要演員和劇組創意人員的姓名會出現。大約90秒鐘後，序列會以標題卡和簡短的片頭來顯示該劇的作者及導演。隨著故事的進行，其結構也發生了變化，新的位置取代了那些功能不太突出或根本沒有的功能<ref name="Art of the Title 2013"/><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130401141737/https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnaxelrod/2013/03/30/how-the-innovative-game-of-thrones-opening-credits-spring-to-life-in-season-3/ |archivedate=2013-04-01 |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnaxelrod/2013/03/30/how-the-innovative-game-of-thrones-opening-credits-spring-to-life-in-season-3/ |title=How The Innovative Game Of Thrones Opening Credits Were Built |work=Forbes |first=John |last=Axelrod |date=2013-03-30 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/race/secrets-game-thrones-opening-credits-179656 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/race/secrets-game-thrones-opening-credits-179656 |title=Secrets Behind 'Game of Thrones' Opening Credits (Video) |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |first=Tim |last=Appelo |date=2011-04-19 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
{{main|{{le|《權力遊戲》系列配樂|Music of Game of Thrones}}}}
[[File:Ramin_Djawadi.jpg|thumb]]為《權力遊戲》撰寫配樂。]]
該系列的配樂由[[拉敏·賈瓦帝|拉敏·賈瓦帝]]作曲。第一季的原聲帶大約在首播十個星期前完成<ref name=Ryan>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110202120407/http://www.aoltv.com/2011/02/02/game-of-thrones/ |archivedate=2011-02-02 |last=Ryan |first=Maureen |title='Game of Thrones' Changes Its Tune, Hires New Composer |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2011/02/02/game-of-thrones/ |accessdate=2011-07-20 |publisher=[[AOL_TV|AOL TV]] |date=2011-02-02}}</ref>，並由{{le|瓦雷澤薩拉班德唱片|Varèse Sarabande}}於2011年6月發行<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725184403/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2011/05/31/game-of-thrones-soundtrack-details/ |archivedate=2016-07-25 |url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2011/05/31/game-of-thrones-soundtrack-details/ |title=Game of Thrones Soundtrack Details |publisher=Film Music Reporter |date=2011-05-31 |accessdate=2011-06-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後各季的原聲配樂專輯經已發行，當中包括了{{le|國民樂隊|The National (band)}}、{{le|保持穩定樂隊|The Hold Steady}}及[[诗格洛丝|席格若斯]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Ramin Djawadi Biography |url=https://www.allmusic.com/artist/ramin-djawadi-mn0000940397 |accessdate=2016-08-29 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829162008/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/ramin-djawadi-mn0000940397 |archivedate=2016-08-29 }}</ref>。賈瓦帝為每個主要家族以及一些主角創作了主題音樂<ref name="Djawadi">{{cite web |url=https://vulture.com/2016/07/game-of-thrones-composer-ramin-djawadi-key-musical-elements.html |title=Game of Thrones Composer Ramin Djawadi on the Show's Key Musical Elements, and That Godfather-esque Finale Tune |first=Jennifer |last=Vineyard |date=2016-07-21 |accessdate=2016-11-06 |work=[[Vulture.com|Vulture]] |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017123724/http://www.vulture.com/2016/07/game-of-thrones-composer-ramin-djawadi-key-musical-elements.html |archivedate=2016-10-17 }}</ref>。主題可能會隨著時間而演變，丹妮莉絲·坦格利安的主題音樂從細小的開始，然後在每季之後變得更加有力。她的主題首先從單一種樂器—[[大提琴|大提琴]]開始，賈瓦帝後來把它結合更多的樂器<ref name="Djawadi"/>。

==== 音效設計 ====
在電視連續劇中不尋常的是，音效團隊收到一個完整季度的粗略剪輯，並以十個小時故事片的形式呈現。儘管第一季和第二季的音效團隊有所不同，但自此是由一個團隊一直負責著音效項目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.asoundeffect.com/creating-the-fantastical-sound-of-game-of-thrones/ |title=This is how the fantastical sound of Game Of Thrones is made |last=Andersen |first=Asbjoern |publisher=A Sound Effect |date=2014-08-06 |accessdate=2014-08-06 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808063046/http://www.asoundeffect.com/creating-the-fantastical-sound-of-game-of-thrones/ |archivedate=2014-08-08 }}</ref>。對於該系列的血腥音效，團隊經常使用到[[臆羚|臆羚]]皮。對於龍的尖叫，交配中的烏龜、海豚、海豹、獅子和鳥的聲音已經使用過<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506065202/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/game-of-thrones-sound-effects |archivedate=2016-05-06 |url=https://vanityfair.com/hollywood/2014/06/game-of-thrones-sound-effects |title=Game of Thrones: The Secrets Behind All the Stabbings, Screams, and Sex Scenes |last=Calautti |first=Katie |work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]] |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2014-08-06 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 語言 ===
《權力遊戲》中的維斯特洛角色都是操英式口音的英語，經常（但不一致）對應於維斯特洛英語地區的角色。北部地區的{{le|愛達德·史塔克|Ned Stark}}以其飾演者肖恩·比恩斯[[約克郡方言|北方本地口音]]說話，而南部領主泰溫·蘭尼斯特（Tywin Lannister）說話帶有[[標準英音|南方的口音]]，而多恩（Dorne）的一眾角色都是操西班牙口音的英語<ref name="Dissecting the real-world accents in Game of Thrones {{!}} Metro News">{{cite web|last=McNeil|first=Colin|title=Dissecting the real-world accents in Game of Thrones {{!}} Metro News|url=http://www.metronews.ca/entertainment/2016/06/24/dialect-coach-dissects-game-of-thrones-accents.html|website=[[Metro_International#North_America|Metro Toronto]]|publisher=Free Daily News Group Inc.|accessdate=2017-04-20|location=Toronto|date=2016-06-24|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170421095418/http://www.metronews.ca/entertainment/2016/06/24/dialect-coach-dissects-game-of-thrones-accents.html|archivedate=2017-04-21}}</ref><ref name="With a wink to its audience,">{{cite web |last1=Epstein |first1=Adam |title=With a wink to its audience, "Game of Thrones" told its most annoying characters to shut up |url=https://qz.com/718066/with-a-wink-to-its-audience-game-of-thrones-told-its-most-annoying-characters-to-shut-up/ |work=[[Quartz_(publication)|Quartz]] |accessdate=2017-04-20  |date=2016-06-27 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170421094509/https://qz.com/718066/with-a-wink-to-its-audience-game-of-thrones-told-its-most-annoying-characters-to-shut-up/ |archivedate=2017-04-21 }}</ref>。維斯特洛人的外來者通常帶有非英式的口音<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://gawker.com/what-is-going-on-with-the-accents-in-game-of-thrones-485816507 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Read |first=Max |title=What Is Going on With the Accents in Game of Thrones? |url=http://gawker.com/what-is-going-on-with-the-accents-in-game-of-thrones-485816507 |accessdate=2013-05-08 |publisher=[[Gawker|Gawker]] |date=2013-05-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

儘管維斯特洛的通用語言都是英語，然而製片人指控語言學家[[大衛·J·彼得森|大衛·J·彼得森]]根據小說中的幾個單詞以構建[[瓦雷利亞語言|瓦雷利亞語言]]及[[多斯拉其語|多斯拉其語]]的[[人工語言|人工語言]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.vulture.com/2013/04/game-of-thrones-dothraki-language-inventor.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Martin |first=Denise |title=Learn to Speak Dothraki and Valyrian From the Man Who Invented Them for Game of Thrones |url=https://vulture.com/2013/04/game-of-thrones-dothraki-language-inventor.html |accessdate=2013-04-24 |newspaper=[[Vulture.com|Vulture]] |date=2013-04-23 |dead-url=no}}</ref>；多斯拉其語和瓦雷利亞語的對話通常配以英語字幕。根據報導，在該系列中的虛構語言較[[威爾斯語|威爾斯語]]、[[愛爾蘭語|愛爾蘭語]]及[[蘇格蘭蓋爾語|蘇格蘭蓋爾語]]結合起來的語言組合被更多的人聽到<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-22461670 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |title=''Game of Thrones'': Can you speak Dothraki? |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-22461670 |accessdate=2013-05-10 |publisher=[[BBC_Radio_4|BBC Radio 4]]|work=[[Today_(BBC_Radio_4)|Today]] |date=2013-05-09 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

