=== IMAX影院 ===
從2015年1月23日開始，《權力遊戲》第四季的最後兩集在美國205個IMAX影院上映；它是首部以這種方式顯示的電視連續劇<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150123092247/http://insidetv.ew.com/2015/01/06/game-of-thrones-imax/ |archivedate=2015-01-23 |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2015/01/06/game-of-thrones-imax/ |title='Game of Thrones' coming to IMAX: First TV series released in format |last=Hibberd |first=James |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2015-01-06 |accessdate=2015-01-22 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。該劇於開畫當天的票房收入為$686,000美元<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828102303/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/box-office-game-of-thrones-eyes-2-million-in-imax-debut-1201420355/ |archivedate=2016-08-28 |url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/box-office-game-of-thrones-eyes-2-million-in-imax-debut-1201420355/ |title=Box Office: 'Game of Thrones' Eyes $2 Million in Imax Debut |first=Maane |last=Khatchatourian |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2015-01-31 |accessdate=2015-02-01 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於開畫周末期間賺得$150萬美元<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421233114/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/02/01/box-office-american-sniper-sets-super-bowl-record-game-of-thrones-scores-in-imax/ |archivedate=2016-04-21 |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/02/01/box-office-american-sniper-sets-super-bowl-record-game-of-thrones-scores-in-imax/ |title=Box Office: 'American Sniper' Sets Super Bowl Record, 'Game Of Thrones' Scores IMAX Touchdown |first=Scott |last=Mendelson |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=2015-02-01 |accessdate=2015-02-01 |dead-url=no}}</ref>；一周的發行總收入為$1,896,092美元<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905171144/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=gameofthronesimax.htm |archivedate=2015-09-05 |url=https://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=gameofthronesimax.htm |title=Game of Thrones (IMAX) (2015) |work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]] |date=2015-02-06 |accessdate=2016-04-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 家庭影院 ===
2012年3月6日，《權力遊戲》第一季的十集以[[DVD|DVD]]和[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]][[Boxset|套裝]]的形式發行。該套裝包括額外的背景和幕後的素材，但沒有刪剪場景，因為這幾乎使用了第一季的所有鏡頭<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017022137/http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/11/30/game-of-thrones-dvd/ |archivedate=2014-10-17 |last=Hibberd |first=James |title='Game of Thrones' scoop: DVD release date, details, photos |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2011/11/30/game-of-thrones-dvd/ |accessdate=2011-12-05 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2011-11-30 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。該套裝在發行後的第一周售出了350,000張，這是HBO系列有史以來最大的首周DVD銷量，該系列創下了HBO系列數碼下載的銷售記錄<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018144145/https://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/16/entertainment-us-tv-gameofthrones-idUSBRE82E1BI20120316 |archivedate=2014-10-18 |last=Richwine |first=Lisa |title='Game of Thrones' rules HBO's DVD sales |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/16/entertainment-us-tv-gameofthrones-idUSBRE82E1BI20120316 |date=2012-03-16 |agency=Reuters |accessdate=2013-03-13 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年11月，該劇發行了收藏版套裝，結合了第一季的DVD和藍光版本以及第二季的第一集。套裝中包括了一個龍蛋形狀的紙鎮<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425203629/http://www.bestbuy.com/site/game-of-thrones-the-complete-first-season-premium-edition-gift-box-8-discs-blu-ray-dvd-blu-ray-disc/6909419.p?id=2541333&skuId=6909419 |archivedate=2016-04-25 |url=http://www.bestbuy.com/site/game-of-thrones-the-complete-first-season-premium-edition-gift-box-8-discs-blu-ray-dvd-blu-ray-disc/6909419.p?id=2541333&skuId=6909419 |title=Game of Thrones: The Complete First Season Premium Edition Gift Box [8 Discs] [Blu-ray/DVD] (Blu-ray Disc) |work=[[Best_Buy|Best Buy]] |date=2012-11-20 |accessdate=2016-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2013年2月19日，第二季的DVD和藍光光碟及數碼下載開始推出<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704025800/http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/11/19/game-of-thrones-season-2-dvd/ |archivedate=2014-07-04 |title='Game of Thrones' season 2 DVD date and extras revealed |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/11/19/game-of-thrones-season-2-dvd/ |accessdate=2013-03-13 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |dead-url=no}}</ref>。套裝的首日銷量打破了HBO的記錄，售出了241,000盒套裝，並下載了355,000集<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030023317/http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/02/22/game-of-thrones-dvd-sales-breaking-hbo-records/ |archivedate=2014-10-30 |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/02/22/game-of-thrones-dvd-sales-breaking-hbo-records/ |title='Game of Thrones' early DVD sales breaking HBO records |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2013-02-22 |accessdate=2013-02-23 |last = Hibberd |first = James |dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三季跟美國首映同時進行，可在澳洲[[ITunes_Store|ITunes Store]]以數碼下載的方式購買，並於2014年2月18日在[[DVD區域碼#區域碼|區域號碼1]]中以DVD和Blu-ray發行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/tv-season/game-of-thrones-season-3/id611198334?ign-mpt=uo%3D4 |title=Game of Thrones season 3 on iTunes Australian Store |publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] |accessdate=2013-03-31 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508105049/https://itunes.apple.com/au/tv-season/game-of-thrones-season-3/id611198334?ign-mpt=uo%3D4 |archivedate=2013-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909203852/http://tvshowsondvd.com/news/Game-Thrones-Season-3/18611|archivedate=2016-09-09|url=http://tvshowsondvd.com/news/Game-Thrones-Season-3/18611|title=Game of Thrones – 2014 Release Date, Package Art for 'The Complete 3rd Season', on DVD, Blu|publisher=TVShowsOnDVD.com|last=Lambert|first=David|date=2013-06-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。第四季於2015年2月17日以DVD和藍光光碟發行<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160908225452/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Game-Thrones-Season-4/20065|archivedate=2016-09-08|url=http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Game-Thrones-Season-4/20065|title=Game of Thrones – 'The Complete 4th Season' Press Release: Date, Art, Cost, Extras|publisher=TVShowsOnDVD.com|last=Lambert|first=David|date=2014-07-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而第五季於2016年3月15日發行<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316093450/http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00VSG3MSC/ |archivedate=2016-03-16 |title=Game of Thrones: Season 5 [Blu-ray + Digital HD] |url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00VSG3MSC/ |accessdate=2015-10-18 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。第六季的DVD和藍光光碟於2016年11月15日發行<ref>{{cite web |title=Game of Thrones: The Complete Sixth Season [Blu-ray] |url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01H2JPULU/ |accessdate=2016-08-29 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130151939/https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01H2JPULU/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年12月12日，第七季發行了DVD和藍光光碟。從2016年開始，HBO開始發行包括{{le|杜比真高清|Dolby TrueHD}}{{le|7.1環迴立體聲|7.1 surround sound}}及[[杜比全景聲|杜比全景聲]]的音頻選項<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.soundandvision.com/content/game-thrones-winter-coming%E2%80%94-atmos |title=Game of Thrones: Winter Is Coming—In Atmos |first=David |last=Vaughn |publisher=Sound & Vision |date=2016-01-29 |accessdate=2017-05-28 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515165338/http://www.soundandvision.com/content/game-thrones-winter-coming%E2%80%94-atmos |archivedate=2016-05-15 }}</ref>。在2018年，第一季以[[4K解析度|4K解像度]]高清的[[超高清藍光光碟|超高清藍光光碟]]發行<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Game-of-Thrones-4K-The-Complete-First-Season-Blu-ray/202472/ |title=Game of Thrones 4K: The Complete First Season Blu-ray |website=Blu-ray.com |accessdate=2019-01-09 |archive-date=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716074719/https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Game-of-Thrones-4K-The-Complete-First-Season-Blu-ray/202472/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 版權侵害 ===
