5-12-28 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226175113/https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-most-torrented-tv-show-of-2016-161226/ |archivedate=2016-12-26 |url=https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-most-torrented-tv-show-of-2016-161226/ |title='Game of Thrones' Most Torrented TV-Show of 2016 |work=[[TorrentFreak|TorrentFreak]] |first=Ernesto |last=Van der Sar |date=2016-12-26 |accessdate=2016-12-26 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-most-torrented-tv-show-of-2017-171226/ |title='Game of Thrones' Most Torrented TV-Show of 2017 |author=Ernesto |work=TorrentFreak |date=2017-12-26 |accessdate=2018-01-02 |archive-date=2020-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302185226/https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-most-torrented-tv-show-of-2017-171226/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-is-the-most-torrented-tv-show-of-2019-191228/ |title=Game of Thrones is the Most Torrented TV-Show of 2019 |date=2019-12-28 |author=Ernesto |website=TorrentFreak |access-date=2020-01-02 |archive-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131210953/https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-is-the-most-torrented-tv-show-of-2019-191228/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2015年第一季，非法下載量增加至約700萬集，比2014年增長了45％<ref name="THR 9 April 2015">{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629121501/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/game-thrones-piracy-soars-season-787594|archivedate=2016-06-29|last=Jarvey|first=Natalie|title='Game of Thrones' Piracy Soars Ahead of Season 5 Premiere|url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/news/game-thrones-piracy-soars-season-787594|accessdate=2015-04-10|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，未命名的一集透過公共[[BitTorrent_tracker|BitTorrent追蹤器]]錄得下載量約為4,280,000次，大約等於其廣播觀眾的數量<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720011942/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20836739 |archivedate=2016-07-20 |title=Game of Thrones tops TV show internet piracy chart |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20836739 |accessdate=2013-01-04 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2012-12-24 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617091847/https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-most-pirated-tv-show-of-2012-121223/ |archivedate=2016-06-17 |title=Game of Thrones Most Pirated TV-Show of 2012 |date=2012-12-23 |work=[[TorrentFreak|TorrentFreak]] |url=https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-most-pirated-tv-show-of-2012-121223/ |accessdate=2012-12-23 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。在澳洲，盜版率也特別高<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160802013734/https://torrentfreak.com/whos-pirating-game-of-thrones-and-why-120520/ |archivedate=2016-08-02 |url=http://torrentfreak.com/whos-pirating-game-of-thrones-and-why-120520/ |title=Who's Pirating Game of Thrones, And Why? |publisher=[[TorrentFreak|TorrentFreak]] |date=2012-05-20 |accessdate=2013-03-31 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，美國駐澳大利亞大使{{le|傑夫·布萊奇|Jeff Bleich}}於2013年發表聲明譴責該系列為於澳洲的盜版<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150125134307/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/us-ambassador-jeffrey-bleich-pleads-australia-stop-pirating-game-of-thrones/story-e6frg6n6-1226629324212 |archivedate=2015-01-25 |last=Piotrowski |first=Daniel |title=US ambassador Jeffrey Bleich pleads: Australia, stop pirating Game of Thrones |url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/us-ambassador-jeffrey-bleich-pleads-australia-stop-pirating-game-of-thrones/story-e6frg6n6-1226629324212 |accessdate=2013-04-25 |work=[[The_Age|The Age]] |date=2013-04-25 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2015年之前，除了HBO及其關聯公司以外，播映方面出現延遲<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508025941/https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2012/05/10/international-audiences-have-few-choices-to-legally-watch-hbos-game-of-thrones/ |archivedate=2016-05-08 |last=Kain |first=Erik |title=International Audiences Have Few Choices To Legally Watch HBO's 'Game Of Thrones' |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2012/05/10/international-audiences-have-few-choices-to-legally-watch-hbos-game-of-thrones/ |accessdate=2012-05-11 |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=2012-05-10 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及這些服務的訂閱費用被認為是該系列非法發行的原因。根據《洪流怪物》的說法，《權力遊戲》的訂閱服務在美國的費用為每月最高$25美元，在英國每集為£26英鎊，並在澳洲每集高達$52澳元<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710144941/https://torrentfreak.com/why-people-pirate-game-of-thrones-a-global-cost-breakdown-140413/ |archivedate=2016-07-10 |title=Why People Pirate Game of Thrones, a Global Cost Breakdown |url=http://torrentfreak.com/why-people-pirate-game-of-thrones-a-global-cost-breakdown-140413/ |accessdate=2014-04-15 |newspaper=[[TorrentFreak|TorrentFreak]] |date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

對於「打擊盜版」，HBO在2013年表示打算在美國首映一周內（包括{{le|HBO Go|HBO Go}}）使其內容更加廣泛<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307224118/https://www.forbes.com/sites/carolpinchefsky/2013/03/04/how-hbo-is-protecting-game-of-thrones-from-online-piracy-in-2013/ |archivedate=2016-03-07 |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/carolpinchefsky/2013/03/04/how-hbo-is-protecting-game-of-thrones-from-online-piracy-in-2013/ |title=How HBO Is Protecting 'Game of Thrones' from Online Piracy in 2013 |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=2013-03-03 |accessdate=2013-03-05 |last = Pinchefsky |first = Carol |dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2015年，[[权力的游戏_(第五季)|第五季]]的[[同步廣播|同步廣播]]覆蓋了170個國家和{{le|HBO Now|HBO Now}}用戶<ref name="THR 9 April 2015" />。4月11日，該季首映的前一天，第五季首四集的{{le|篩選器|Screener (promotional)}}副本洩漏到[[檔案分享|檔案分享]]網站<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626183441/http://gizmodo.com/nearly-half-of-game-of-thrones-season-5-just-leaked-1697305966 |archivedate=2016-06-26 |title=Nearly Half of Game of Thrones Season 5 Just Leaked |url=https://gizmodo.com/nearly-half-of-game-of-thrones-season-5-just-leaked-1697305966 |website=Gizmodo |dead-url=no}}</ref>。在洩漏的一天之內，文件被下載了80萬次以上<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412204649/https://www.forbes.com/sites/josephsteinberg/2015/04/12/upcoming-game-of-thrones-episodes-leak-online-was-hbo-hacked/ |archivedate=2016-04-12 |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/josephsteinberg/2015/04/12/upcoming-game-of-thrones-episodes-leak-online-was-hbo-hacked/ |title=Nearly Half Of 'Game of Thrones' Upcoming Season Leaks Online – Was HBO Hacked? |date=2015-04-12 |first=Joseph |last=Steinberg |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |accessdate=2015-04-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref>；在一個星期內，非法下載量已達到3,200萬次，僅次於第五季首映（[[戰爭來臨|戰爭來臨]]）的盜版次數達1,300萬<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307001526/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-season-5-breaks-piracy-record-with-32m-illegal-downloads-10197482.html |archivedate=2016-03-07 |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/game-of-thrones-season-5-breaks-piracy-record-with-32m-illegal-downloads-10197482.html |title=Game of Thrones season 5 breaks piracy record with 32m illegal downloads |first=Jess |last=Denham |date=2015-04-23 |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |accessdate=2015-05-12 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。第五季的結局《{{le|母親的慈悲|Mother's Mercy}}》是史上[[BitTorrent_(協定)|BitTorrent協議]]文件共享協議上最多同時共享的文件，擁有超過25萬名同時共享者，在8個小時內下載量超過150萬次<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811132514/https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-season-finale-breaks-piracy-record-150615/ |archivedate=2016-08-11 |url=https://torrentfreak.com/game-of-thrones-season-finale-breaks-piracy-record-150615/ |title=Game of Thrones Season Finale breaks Piracy Records |publisher=[[TorrentFreak|TorrentFreak]] |date=2015-06-15 |accessdate=2015-06-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。至於第六季，HBO並未將{{le|篩選器|Screener (promotional)}}發送給媒體，以防止未經許可的副本傳播和[[劇透|劇透]]<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415083105/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/03/02/game-thrones-season-6-review-screeners |archivedate=2016-04-15 |url=https://ew.com/article/2016/03/02/game-thrones-season-6-review-screeners |title=''Game of Thrones'' lockdown: HBO won't send press any season 6 episodes |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=2016-03-02 |accessdate=2016-03-02 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一些觀察員，包括系列的導演{{le|大衛·彼得拉卡|David Petrarca}}<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318180807/http://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/tv-and-radio/downloads-dont-matter-20130226-2f36r.html |archivedate=2016-03-18 |url=https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/tv-and-radio/downloads-dont-matter-20130226-2f36r.html |title=Downloads don't matter |work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |date=2013-02-26 |accessdate=2013-03-02 |agency=Australian Associated Press |dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[華納媒體|華納媒體]]的CEO{{le|傑夫·貝克斯|Jeff Bewkes}}說，非法下載並沒有損害該系列的前景；它得益於[[口耳相傳|口碑行銷]]及社交評論，高盜版率並沒有明顯地導致訂戶流失。根據《[[Polygon|Polygon]]》的說法，HBO對盜版和共享登錄憑據的寬鬆態度構成了高級電視的[[网络游戏免费模式|網絡遊戲免費模式]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308073846/http://www.polygon.com/2014/4/21/5636120/game-of-thrones-free-to-play-tv-hbo |archivedate=2016-03-08 |last=Kuchera |first=Ben |title=Game of Thrones is the first 'free-to-play' TV show, and gaming is racing to catch up |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/4/21/5636120/game-of-thrones-free-to-play-tv-hbo |accessdate=2014-04-21 |newspaper=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |date=2014-04-21 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2015年的[[牛津大學辯論社|牛津大學辯論社]]的辯論大賽中，該系列的共同創作者大衛·貝尼奧夫說自己很高興看到人們觀賞該系列；非法下載的劇集有時會讓感興趣的觀眾足以購買一份副本，尤其是在沒有播放《權力遊戲》的國家。共同創作者魏斯對此百感交集，說這個系列製作起來很貴，和「如果不能賺回本錢，那麼它就不再存在了」。然而，他對如此多的人「非常喜歡這個劇集，他們迫不及待地想要把它拿在自己手中」一事感到很高興<ref>{{cite web |title=Game of Thrones at the Oxford Union – Full Address |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfvVluNxujc |via=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |accessdate=2015-06-15 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601173130/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfvVluNxujc |archivedate=2015-06-01 }}</ref>。2015年，《[[健力士世界紀錄|健力士世界紀錄]]》把《權力遊戲》命名為最多盜版的電視節目<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603142753/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2015/8/maisie-williams-overjoyed-as-game-of-thrones-marches-into-guinness-world-records-394562 |archivedate=2016-06-03 |url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2015/8/maisie-williams-overjoyed-as-game-of-thrones-marches-into-guinness-world-records-394562 |title=Maisie Williams overjoyed as Game of Thrones marches into Guinness World Records 2016 |work=[[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records]] |last=Lynch |first=Kevin |date=2015-08-31 |accessdate=2015-11-11 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 回響 ==
在首映之前，《權力遊戲》受到一眾粉絲的高度期待<ref>{{Cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120193535/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2010/jul/22/game-of-thrones-most-anticipated |archivedate=2011-11-20 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2010/jul/22/game-of-thrones-most-anticipated |title=Is A Game of Thrones the most eagerly anticipated TV show ever? |date=2010-07-23 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |first=Mathilda |last=Gregory |accessdate=2013-03-13 |location=London |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2010/08/with-game-of-thrones-hbo-is-plotting-for-another-true-blood.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Colins |first=Scott |title=With 'Game of Thrones,' HBO is playing for another 'True Blood' |date=2010-08-08 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2010/08/with-game-of-thrones-hbo-is-plotting-for-another-true-blood.html |accessdate=2013-03-13 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且已成為關鍵性商業上的成功。根據《[[衛報|衛報]]》的說法，它成為了電視上的「重頭戲」及「備受關注的節目」<ref name="The Guardian March 22, 2014">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920154652/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/mar/22/game-of-thrones-whats-not-to-love |archivedate=2016-09-20 |last=Hughes |first=Sarah |title='Sopranos meets Middle-earth': how Game of Thrones took over our world |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/mar/22/game-of-thrones-whats-not-to-love |accessdate=2014-03-22 |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2014-03-22 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[好莱坞报道|荷李活報道]]》於2015年對2,800名演員、製片人、導演和其他行業人士進行的調查顯示，他們把《權力遊戲》列為最喜歡的節目第四位<ref name="thr20150916">{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/best-tv-shows-ever-top-819499/item/friends-hollywoods-100-favorite-tv-821361 |title=Hollywood's 100 Favorite TV Shows |date=2015-09-16 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2019-07-17 |language=en |archive-date=2019-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717030112/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/best-tv-shows-ever-top-819499/item/friends-hollywoods-100-favorite-tv-821361 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 文化影響 ===
儘管《權力遊戲》被一些影評人不屑一顧<ref name="The Guardian March 22, 2014"/>，然而它的成功是歸功於[[奇幻作品|奇幻]]類型作品的流行度增加。根據[[有線電視新聞網|CNN]]的報導，在[[冰與火之歌：權力遊戲_(第二季)|第二季]]首播前夕，「在這個周末之後，你可能會很難找到不是某種[[古典奇幻|古典奇幻]]粉絲的人」，它並引用{{le|伊恩·波哥斯特|Ian Bogost}}的話語，說該系列劇集延續了自2001年[[彼得·杰克逊|彼德·積遜]]的《[[魔戒電影三部曲|魔戒電影三部曲]]》開始的成功改編趨勢，以及《[[哈利波特系列電影|哈利波特系列電影]]》將幻想類電影確立為大眾市場類型；它們都是「幻想類粉絲文化的誘導性毒品」<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927162257/http://geekout.blogs.cnn.com/2012/03/30/mainstream-finally-believes-fantasy-fans/ |archivedate=2016-09-27 |last=Williams |first=Joel |title=Mainstream finally believes fantasy fans |url=http://geekout.blogs.cnn.com/2012/03/30/mainstream-finally-believes-fantasy-fans/ |accessdate=2012-04-05 |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |date=2012-03-30 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。劇集的成功導致電視台播放許多幻想系列，包括{{le|阿瑪遜工作室|Amazon Studios}}的《魔戒》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vulture.com/2019/03/lord-of-the-rings-amazon-maps.html |title=Amazon's Lord of the Rings Series: What Is the Second Age? |work=Vulture |date=2019-03-11 |accessdate=2019-04-10 |archive-date=2020-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301164359/https://www.vulture.com/2019/03/lord-of-the-rings-amazon-maps.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[尼爾·蓋曼|尼爾·蓋曼]]的說法，他的《[[好預兆_(迷你劇)|好預兆]]》及《[[美國眾神_(電視劇)|美國眾神]]》都被改編成為電視劇，《權力遊戲》確實有助改變電視上對幻想作品的態度，但它主要地讓幻想系列的巨額預算更能被接受<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/apr/01/whats-the-next-game-of-thrones-all-the-contenders-for-fantasy-tvs-crown |title=What's the next Game of Thrones? All the contenders for fantasy TV's crown |first=Sarah |last=Hughes |date=2019-04-01 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2019-04-10 |archive-date=2020-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318102418/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/apr/01/whats-the-next-game-of-thrones-all-the-contenders-for-fantasy-tvs-crown |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這種類型的成功歸功於作家們在流行文化中對逃避現實的嚮往，經常有女性裸露身體，以及平衡輕鬆愉快和嚴肅話題（例如龍與政治）的技巧，這使它成為享有傳統聲望的頂級戲劇系列<ref name="The Guardian March 22, 2014" />。

該系列的受歡迎程度讓《[[冰與火之歌|冰與火之歌]]》小說的銷售（以配對形式再版）有所提高，使它持續成為該類別的暢銷書榜榜首幾個月。根據《[[每日野獸|每日野獸]]》的報導，《權力遊戲》是[[情景喜剧|處境喜劇]]作者的最愛，而該系列在其他電視連續劇中都曾被提及過<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/09/21/game-of-thrones-modern-family-parks-and-rec-writers-on-why-they-love-the-hbo-drama.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Lacob |first=Jace |title='Game of Thrones': 'Modern Family,' 'Parks and Rec' Writers on Why They Love the HBO Drama |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2012/09/21/game-of-thrones-modern-family-parks-and-rec-writers-on-why-they-love-the-hbo-drama.html |accessdate=2012-09-27 |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Beast|The Daily Beast]] |date=2012-09-21 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。在其他幻想系列中，它被認為是增加購買（和遺棄）[[哈士奇|哈士奇]]犬及其他類似狼的狗的原因<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.independent.co.uk/environment/nature/game-of-thrones-inspired-huskie-craze-goes-cold-as-owners-give-up-on-dogs-8431188.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=O'Brian |first=Liam |title=Game of Thrones inspired Huskie craze goes cold as owners give up on dogs |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/environment/nature/game-of-thrones-inspired-huskie-craze-goes-cold-as-owners-give-up-on-dogs-8431188.html |accessdate=2013-03-10 |newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=2012-12-26 |location=London |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

流行詞彙中已新增《權力遊戲》的字詞。在第一季中，{{le|彼得·貝利甚|Petyr Baelish}}解釋了當妓女在背景中發生性行為，他的動機（或背景）產生了單詞「{{le|性姿勢|Sexposition}}」，用以提供性愛與裸露的解說<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328073923/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/mar/11/sexposition-story-tv-drama |archivedate=2013-03-28 |last=Hann |first=Michael |title=How 'sexposition' fleshes out the story |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2012/mar/11/sexposition-story-tv-drama? |accessdate=2012-03-29 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2012-03-11 |location=London |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該系列的游牧騎兵—[[冰與火之歌的世界|多斯拉其]]於2012年9月的「{{le|全球語言監控器|Global Language Monitor}}」中，互聯網上使用最多來自電視的單詞表中排名第四<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://entertainment.time.com/2012/09/25/and-the-top-television-words-of-the-year-are/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Steinmetz |first=Kate |title=And the Top TV Words of the Year Are{{nbsp}}... |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2012/09/25/and-the-top-television-words-of-the-year-are/ |accessdate=2012-09-27 |newspaper=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |date=2012-09-25 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2012年，媒體使用《權力遊戲》作為激烈衝突和欺騙情況的一種比喻或比較，例如[[全國獨立企業聯盟訴西貝利厄斯案|全國獨立企業聯盟訴西貝利厄斯案]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/ray-brescia/game-of-robes-why-conserv_b_1647678.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Brescia |first=Ray |title=Game of Robes: Why Conservatives May Ultimately Praise the Roberts Switch on Health Care Reform |url=https://huffingtonpost.com/ray-brescia/game-of-robes-why-conserv_b_1647678.html |accessdate=2012-07-07 |newspaper=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]] |date=2012-07-06 |dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/martin-varsavsky/there-is-still-a-lot-of-g_b_1649089.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Varsavsky |first=Martin |title=The Game of Thrones Around Us |url=https://huffingtonpost.com/martin-varsavsky/there-is-still-a-lot-of-g_b_1649089.html |accessdate=2012-07-07 |newspaper=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]] |date=2012-07-04 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及[[薄熙來|薄熙來]]被中國政府罷免事件<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.theage.com.au/world/strongmen-of-china-playing-a-risky-game-of-thrones-20120630-219km.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Garnaut |first=John |title=Strongmen of China playing a risky game of thrones |url=http://www.theage.com.au/world/strongmen-of-china-playing-a-risky-game-of-thrones-20120630-219km.html |accessdate=2012-07-07 |newspaper=[[The_Age|The Age]] |date=2012-07-01 |location=Melbourne |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年，唱作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]告訴《[[娱乐周刊|娛樂週刊]]》指她於2017年的專輯《[[舉世盛名|舉世盛名]]》中，有幾首歌曲的靈感都是來自《權力遊戲》中的角色和情節<ref>{{cite news |url=https://ew.com/music/2019/05/09/taylor-swift-game-of-thrones-reputation/ |title=Taylor Swift reveals how ''Game of Thrones'' (and Arya's kill list) inspired ''reputation'' |last=Suskind |first=Alex |date=2019-05-09 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |accessdate=2019-05-10 |archive-date=2019-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509205342/https://ew.com/music/2019/05/09/taylor-swift-game-of-thrones-reputation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美國，以「Khaleesi」為女嬰的名字變得越來越流行。在小說和電視劇中，「khaleesi」並非名字，而是[[丹妮莉絲·坦格利安|丹妮莉絲·坦格利安]]持有的[[多斯拉其語|多斯拉其語]]中可汗（軍閥）妻子的頭銜<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819190426/http://www.cbc.ca/newsblogs/yourcommunity/2014/04/there-are-now-more-babies-named-khaleesi-than-betsy-or-nadine-in-the-us.html |archivedate=2016-08-19 |last=O'Neil |first=Lauren |title=There are now more babies named 'Khaleesi' than 'Betsy' or 'Nadine' in the U.S. |url=http://www.cbc.ca/newsblogs/yourcommunity/2014/04/there-are-now-more-babies-named-khaleesi-than-betsy-or-nadine-in-the-us.html |date=2014-04-11 |publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]] |accessdate=2016-04-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《權力遊戲》也已成為科學探究的主題<ref name="pmid27065510">{{cite journal |vauthors=Scharl A, Hubmann-Haidvogel A, Jones A, Fischl D, Kamolov R, Weichselbraun A, Rafelsberger W |title=Analyzing the public discourse on works of fiction - Detection and visualization of emotion in online coverage about HBO's Game of Thrones |journal=Information Processing and Management |year=2016 |volume=52 |issue=1 |pages=129–138 |doi=10.1016/j.ipm.2015.02.003 |pmid=27065510 |pmc=4804387}}</ref><ref name="pmid27532353">{{cite journal |vauthors=Lipoff JB |title=Greyscale-A Mystery Dermatologic Disease on HBO's Game of Thrones |journal=JAMA Dermatology |year=2016 |volume=152 |issue=8 |pages=904 |doi=10.1001/jamadermatol.2015.5793 |pmid=27532353}}</ref><ref name="pmid30535868">{{cite journal |vauthors=Lystad RP, Brown BT |title=Death is certain, the time is not: mortality and survival in Game of Thrones |journal=Injury Epidemiology |year=2018 |volume=5 |pages=44 |doi=10.1186/s40621-018-0174-7 |pmid=30535868|pmc=6286904 }}</ref>。2016年，研究人員發表了一篇論文，分析了於[[权力的游戏_(第四季)|第四季]]期間，在網絡公共話語中與展開的故事情節相關的情緒情感<ref name="pmid27065510"/>。該分析據稱能夠將有關故事情節的討論與媒體評論或對特定演員的表現的評估區分開。2018年，澳洲科學家進行了一項[[生存分析|生存分析]]，並研究了《權力遊戲》的首七季中330個重要角色的死亡率<ref name="pmid30535868"/>。2019年，[[國際紅十字與紅新月運動|國際紅十字會]]的澳洲分會進行了一項使用[[戰爭法|國際人權法]]，以確定哪個角色在演出首七個季度中，干犯了最多的[[戰爭罪|戰爭罪]]行<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.militarytimes.com/off-duty/military-culture/2019/04/11/the-worst-war-criminals-in-game-of-thrones-ranked/ |title=The worst war criminals in 'Game of Thrones' ranked |last=Simkins |first=J.D. |date=2019-04-11 |work=[[Sightline_Media_Group|Military Times]] |accessdate=2019-04-12 |archive-date=2019-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417171000/https://www.militarytimes.com/off-duty/military-culture/2019/04/11/the-worst-war-criminals-in-game-of-thrones-ranked/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

