《權力遊戲》特別是在首七個季度，儘管該系列頻繁使用裸露和暴力鏡頭而遭到批評，然而獲得廣泛好評。其季度曾出現於2011年《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》、2011年及2012年的《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》及2012年的《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》出版之年度「最佳」列表<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130305075523/http://winter-is-coming.net/2011/12/thrones-lands-on-tons-of-top-tv-shows-of-2011-lists/ |archivedate=2013-03-05 |title=Thrones lands on tons of top TV shows of 2011 lists |url=http://winter-is-coming.net/2011/12/thrones-lands-on-tons-of-top-tv-shows-of-2011-lists/ |publisher=WinterIsComing.net |date=2011-12-23 |accessdate=2011-12-23 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://grrm.livejournal.com/255830.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Martin |first=George R. R. |title=Plaudits for GAME OF THRONES |url=http://grrm.livejournal.com/255830.html |accessdate=2011-12-23 |date=2011-12-21 |publisher=Not A Blog |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411133825/http://winteriscoming.net/2012/12/game-of-thrones-the-best-of-2012/ |archivedate=2014-04-11 |title=Game of Thrones: The best of 2012 |url=http://winteriscoming.net/2012/12/game-of-thrones-the-best-of-2012/ |accessdate=2013-01-04 |publisher=WinterIsComing.net |date=2012-12-27 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，該系列於《[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]》的評價為89％<ref name="RottenTomatoesS3" />。

演員團隊的表現受到讚賞。[[彼特·丁拉基|彼特·丁拉基]]的「魅力、在道德上模棱兩可和自我意識」<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304230144/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2011/04/15/hbos_game_of_thrones_is_fantastical/ |archivedate=2016-03-04 |last=Gilbert |first=Matthew |title=Fantasy comes true with HBO's 'Game of Thrones' |url=https://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2011/04/15/hbos_game_of_thrones_is_fantastical/ |accessdate=2013-05-19 |newspaper=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]] |date=2011-04-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。提利昂為自己贏得[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]及[[金球獎|金球獎]]的獎項，尤其受人關注。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的瑪麗·麥克納馬拉（Mary McNamara）於提利昂成為系列[[权力的游戏_(第二季)|第二季]]的中心人物之前寫道：「從許多方面來說，《權力遊戲》都屬於丁克拉格<ref name="Los Angeles Times April 15, 2011">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/apr/15/entertainment/la-et-game-of-thrones-review-20110415 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=McNamara |first=Mary |title=Swords, sex and struggles |url=https://articles.latimes.com/2011/apr/15/entertainment/la-et-game-of-thrones-review-20110415 |accessdate=2013-05-19 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2011-04-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329120407/http://www.salon.com/2012/03/29/bloody_bloody_game_of_thrones/singleton/ |archivedate=2012-03-29 |last=Paskin |first=Willa |title=Bloody, bloody "Game of Thrones" |url=http://www.salon.com/2012/03/29/bloody_bloody_game_of_thrones/singleton/ |accessdate=2013-05-19 |newspaper=[[Salon_magazine|Salon]] |date=2012-03-29}}</ref>。」一些評論家強調了眾女演員<ref name="Los Angeles Times April 15, 2011" />和兒童演員們的表現<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821120407/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Roush-Review-Thrones-1031879.aspx |archivedate=2014-08-21 |url=https://tvguide.com/News/Roush-Review-Thrones-1031879.aspx |title=Roush Review: Grim Thrones Is a Crowning Achievement |first=Matt |last=Roush |work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]] |date=2011-04-15 |accessdate=2011-05-11 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。14歲的[[麦茜·威廉姆斯|梅西·威廉斯]]在首季以{{le|艾莉亞·史塔克|Arya Stark}}的角色出道，並在第二季跟資深演員[[查尔斯·丹斯|查理斯·丹士]]（{{le|泰溫·蘭尼斯特|Tywin Lannister}}）被挑選出來為其角色於第二季演出<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/lists/game-changers-the-10-biggest-changes-between-game-of-thrones-and-the-books-20120515/the-tywin-and-arya-show-19691231 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |title=The Tywin and Arya Show |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/lists/game-changers-the-10-biggest-changes-between-game-of-thrones-and-the-books-20120515/the-tywin-and-arya-show-19691231 |accessdate=2013-05-19 |newspaper=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] |date=2012-05-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[斯蒂芬·迪蘭|斯蒂芬·迪蘭]]作為{{le|斯坦尼斯·巴拉森|Stannis Baratheon}}的表現受到好評，尤其是在[[权力的游戏_(第五季)|第五季]]中，一位評論家指出：「無論你是否喜歡斯坦尼斯，你都必須承認斯蒂芬·迪蘭於今季表現出色<ref>{{cite web |url=http://decider.com/2015/06/15/game-of-thrones-s5-finale-recap/ |title=Death! Despair! Dragons! How The 'Game of Thrones' Finale Changed The Game For Everyone |date=2015-06-15 |work=Decider |accessdate=2017-11-30 |archive-date=2020-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324101528/https://decider.com/2015/06/15/game-of-thrones-s5-finale-recap/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

另外,席恩·葛雷喬伊(Theon Greyjoy)飾演者[[阿爾菲·阿倫|阿爾菲·阿倫]](Alfie Allen)的演技同樣受到劇組上下高度讚賞。[[基特·哈靈頓|基特·哈靈頓]]表示：「席恩是非常難演的角色，我無法比阿爾菲做得更好。阿爾菲完全掌控住他。」[[蘇菲·特納|蘇菲·特納]]說：「阿爾菲是個非常認真且對角色傾注所有心血的演員。有時候拍到你的特寫部分，你的對手戲演員只會站在對面敷衍下，我也明白他們不想在這種事情上浪費感情…但阿爾菲每一次都會很認真投入去演，這樣我很感動，甚至好幾次都不自覺的掉眼淚。」[[丹尼爾·波特曼|丹尼爾·波特曼]]說:「阿爾菲是個天才。他是我一生中見過的最好的演員之一，他把席恩的轉變過程演釋得非常出色。」導演Alik Sakharov指出:「阿爾菲的臉部表情很棒。眼睛像能說話一樣。他的眼睛告訴你的事遠遠超過了你所看到的。我的意思是，他完全掌控住了。對於一個普通演員來說，尤其是在這樣的遠景中，您會想節省能量，因為觀眾甚至不會注意到你。但阿爾菲卻全力以赴去演。這太棒了。」

值得一提的是，第五季拉姆斯對珊莎施暴一幕中，阿爾菲(席恩)有一個長達20秒的特寫鏡頭。其實一開始導演並沒打算使用特寫鏡頭的(而是打算使用wide shot遠鏡)。因為正式拍攝的時候，阿爾菲的表情反應過於強烈(引用導演的話是:像沒有明天一樣崩潰地抽泣著[breaks down on screen, sobbing like there's no tomorrow.])，導演[[Jeremy_Podeswa|Jeremy Podeswa]]看到阿爾菲的表演後，立即決定改用特寫鏡頭。此外,編導[[傑里米·波德斯瓦|傑里米·波德斯瓦]]、[[大衛·班紐夫|大衛·班紐夫]]、[[丹尼爾·威斯|丹尼爾·威斯]]、[[布萊恩·考克曼|布萊恩·考克曼]]、[[阿歷克斯·格雷夫斯|阿歷克斯·格雷夫斯]]，演員[[琳娜·海蒂|琳娜·海蒂]]、[[娜塔莉·多莫|娜塔莉·多莫]]、[[伊萬·瑞恩|伊萬·瑞恩]]等人都曾公開讚賞[[阿爾菲·阿倫|阿爾菲·阿倫]]的演技和對演戲的認真態度。

至於拉姆斯·波頓飾演者[[伊萬·瑞恩|伊萬·瑞恩]]的演技同樣受好評。監製[[大衛·班紐夫|大衛·班紐夫]]、[[丹尼爾·威斯|丹尼爾·威斯]]表示:「伊萬是個很棒的演員，相信將來他還有很棒的演出機會等著他。他並不是那種典型只能演壞人的演員，事實上我們第一次見到他時，他是來試鏡瓊恩的角色，他的表演可以隨機應變，而這也是他有趣的地方。拉姆斯不只是個呲牙裂嘴的可惡反派，每句台詞從他的口中說出時都讓人驚喜，看他表演感覺很棒，這個角色原來可能會很無聊，不過在他的詮釋下卻非常有趣，他實在演得太壞了，壞到沒藥醫。」<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2016/08/game-of-thrones-david-benioff-d-b-weiss-emmys-interview-1201803698/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2020-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223024947/https://deadline.com/2016/08/game-of-thrones-david-benioff-d-b-weiss-emmys-interview-1201803698/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>導演亞力克·沙克羅夫表示:「[[伊萬·瑞恩|伊萬·瑞恩]]和[[阿爾菲·阿倫|阿爾菲·阿倫]]一樣厲害。所以他們的每一場對手戲都很棒。他們兩個有種強烈的化學反應。當他們彼此看著對方時（或者不看對方時），你都會覺得:「啊糟透了！」他倆的表演完完全全牽動觀眾的情緒。 」<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-director-bathtub-scene-703135 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archive-date=2020-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223031415/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-director-bathtub-scene-703135 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第一季的評論者表示該系列具有很高的生產價值，一個完全實現的世界和引人注目的角色<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017221329/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20481542%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-10-17 |last = Tucker |first = Ken |title=Game of Thrones (2011) |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2011-04-14 |accessdate=2011-05-11 |url=https://ew.com/ew/article/0,,20481542,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的說法，「對於HBO來說，其網絡上沒有比《權力遊戲》更有利可圖的內容了。僅僅在一個季度之後全由付費有線電視製作，這已經是全球性的現象，幻想片的糾紛是一場回報豐厚的賭博<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://variety.com/2011/tv/news/cablers-hit-highs-lows-pr-hurdles-in-2011-1118047923/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://variety.com/2011/tv/news/cablers-hit-highs-lows-pr-hurdles-in-2011-1118047923/ |title=Cablers hit highs, lows, PR hurdles in 2011 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2011-12-27 |accessdate=2011-12-31 |last = Levine |first = Stuart |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。」第二季也很受歡迎，《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》讚賞其「生動、生氣勃勃的和只是普通有趣」的說故事<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027041802/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20470532_20580368%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-10-27 |last=Tucker |first=Ken |title=TV Review: Game Of Thrones (2012) |url=https://ew.com/ew/article/0,,20470532_20580368,00.html |accessdate=2012-03-25 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2012-03-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且，根據《[[荷里活報道|荷李活報道]]》所述，該劇集系列取得「成為最佳劇集系列之一的充分理由」；其嚴肅性使其成為唯一可與《[[广告狂人|廣告狂人]]》和《[[絕命毒師|絕命毒師]]》互相媲美的戲劇<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6W4Uf7zgs?url=http://edit.hollywoodreporter.com/review/Game-of-Thrones-HBO-Peter-Dinklage-George-Martin-304869 |archivedate=2015-02-03 |last=Goodman |first=Tim |title='Game of Thrones' Season 2: TV Review |url=http://edit.hollywoodreporter.com/review/Game-of-Thrones-HBO-Peter-Dinklage-George-Martin-304869 |accessdate=2012-03-28 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2012-03-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》對該系列發表了褒貶不一的評價，批評其角色的數量、缺乏複雜性和迂迴曲折的情節<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921082549/http://tv.nytimes.com/2012/03/30/arts/television/game-of-thrones-on-hbo.html |archivedate=2013-09-21 |last=Genzlinger |first=Neil |title=Uneasy Lies the Head That Steals a Crown: 'Game of Thrones' on HBO |url=http://tv.nytimes.com/2012/03/30/arts/television/game-of-thrones-on-hbo.html |accessdate=2012-03-29 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2012-03-29 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第三季受到評論家的極度好評，《Metacritic》給它91分（滿分為100分），表示「普遍讚譽」<ref name="MetacriticS3" />。第四季同樣得到讚揚；《Metacritic》根據29條評論給它評分為94／100，再次表示為「普遍讚譽」<ref name="MetacriticS4" />。第五季也受到評論家的好評，在《Metacritic》上基於29個評論，得分為91／100<ref name="MetacriticS5" />。第六季的評價儘管不如其前作那麼高，但也得到評論家的稱讚，它在《Metacritic》上基於9個評論，其得分為73分，表示為「總體上好評」<ref name="MetacriticS6" />。第七季基於12個評論得到77／100的評分，並因其動作戲及重點突出中心人物而受到讚譽<ref name="MetacriticS7" />，但因其突破性的步伐和情節發展「違背邏輯」而受到批評<ref name="RottenTomatoesS7"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/8/14/16143576/game-of-thrones-season-seven-eastwatch-hbo |title=Game of Thrones' current breakneck pace is gutting its most anticipated reunions |work=The Verge |first=Megan |last=Farokhmanesh |date=2017-08-14 |accessdate=2017-11-30 |archive-date=2020-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324101523/https://www.theverge.com/2017/8/14/16143576/game-of-thrones-season-seven-eastwatch-hbo |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娛樂週刊]]》的達倫·弗朗希（Darren Franich）給予該系列評為「B級」，表示該系列最終「還可以」，既有「超越瞬間」和「悲慘的階段」，它「被人深愛到足以被每個人為某件事作出批評」。弗朗希把第3季和第4季描述為「無情」，第6季的結局是「殺手一拳兩擊」，而第7和第8季都是「不感興趣的」<ref>{{cite web |last1=Franich |first1=Darren |title=Game of Thrones was… okay: EW review |url=https://ew.com/tv-reviews/2019/05/20/game-of-thrones-finale-series-review/ |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2019-05-20 |accessdate=2019-05-24 |archive-date=2019-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523200024/https://ew.com/tv-reviews/2019/05/20/game-of-thrones-finale-series-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 性愛與暴力 ====
儘管劇評人對此劇表示熱烈歡迎，他們中有些人批評該劇所描繪的女性裸體、暴力和性暴力的數量，以及描述這些主題的方式。《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋雜誌]]》稱該系列改編原材料的「決定性弱點」是「傾向於增加性愛和暴力，尤其是性暴力<ref name="Atlantic">{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826014749/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2015/05/game-of-thrones-roundtable-season-5-episode-six-unbowed-unbent-unbroken/393503/ |archivedate=2016-08-26 |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2015/05/game-of-thrones-roundtable-season-5-episode-six-unbowed-unbent-unbroken/393503/ |title=Game of Thrones: A Pointless Horror and a Ridiculous Fight |last=Kornhaber |first=Spencer |last2=Orr |first2=Christopher |last3=Sullivan |first3=Amy |work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] |date=2015-05-17 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。」馬田回答說，他認為必須對歷史和人性誠實，而且強姦和性暴力在戰爭中很普遍；如果將它從敘述中省略，那將是虛假的，並破壞了其歷史現實主義的[[#主題|小說主題]]<ref name="New York Times May 2, 2014" />。HBO表示他們「完全支持丹和大衛對傑出作品的視野和藝術性，我們認為這項作品不言自明<ref name="New York Times May 2, 2014" />。」

系列中的性愛和裸露數量，尤其是在劇情附帶的場景中，許多批評都集中針對系列中的[[权力的游戏_(第一季)|第一季]]和[[权力的游戏_(第二季)|第二季]]。飾演{{le|斯坦尼斯·巴拉森|Stannis Baratheon}}的[[斯蒂芬·迪蘭|斯蒂芬·迪蘭]]，把該系列的頻繁的露骨場景比擬作為「1970年代的德國色情片」<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/01/14/game-of-thrones-stephen-dillane-the-tunnel_n_4595628.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Frost |first=Caroline |title='Game of Thrones' Star Stephen Dillane Admits the Nudity Is Like 'German Porn from the 1970s' |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/01/14/game-of-thrones-stephen-dillane-the-tunnel_n_4595628.html |accessdate=2014-01-16 |newspaper=[[HuffPost|HuffPost]] |date=2014-01-14 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|查莉·珍·安德斯|Charlie Jane Anders}}於《{{le|io9|io9}}》中寫道：雖然第一季充滿了輕鬆的「性愛」，而第二季似乎集中於令人討厭的，剝削的和非人性化性愛，然而很少的信息內容<ref name="io9 2 May 2012">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911064821/http://io9.com/5906540/is-game-of-thrones-gratiutious-sex-worse-than-the-gratuitous-violence |archivedate=2015-09-11 |last=Anders |first=Charlie Jane |title=Is Game of Thrones' gratuitous sex worse than the gratuitous violence? |url=http://io9.com/5906540/is-game-of-thrones-gratiutious-sex-worse-than-the-gratuitous-violence |accessdate=2012-05-02 |website=[[io9|io9]] |date=2012-05-02 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根據《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的安娜·霍姆斯（Anna Holmes）的說法，這些裸露的場景似乎主要是針對挑逗異性戀的男性，一直到該系列仿中世紀設定中的女性所喜愛的巴西蠟，使這些場景與其他觀眾疏遠了<ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Anna |title=Skin is wearing thin on HBO's 'Game of Thrones' |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/skin-is-wearing-thin-on-hbos-game-of-thrones/2012/04/26/gIQA4hd6jT_story_1.html |accessdate=2012-05-02 |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=2012-04-26 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527173457/http://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/skin-is-wearing-thin-on-hbos-game-of-thrones/2012/04/26/gIQA4hd6jT_story_1.html |archivedate=2012-05-27 }}</ref>。《[[赫芬顿邮报|哈芬登郵報]]》的莫琳·瑞安（Maureen Ryan）同樣指出，《權力遊戲》主要呈現的是裸體女性，而不是男性，而且多餘的「隨機乳房」削弱了該系列可能要解決封建社會中對婦女壓迫而可能產生的任何抱負<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502120407/http://www.aoltv.com/2011/05/29/game-of-thrones-season-1-episode-7-recap/ |archivedate=2012-05-02 |last=Ryan |first=Maureen |title='Game of Thrones' Season 1, Episode 7 Recap |url=http://www.aoltv.com/2011/05/29/game-of-thrones-season-1-episode-7-recap/ |accessdate=2012-05-02 |publisher=[[AOL_TV|AOL TV]] |date=2011-05-29}}</ref>。《[[周六夜现场|週六夜現場]]》在草圖中滑稽地模仿這一方面的改編，將該系列描繪為保留一名13歲男孩當顧問，其主要關注點是盡可能顯示最多乳房越好<ref name="io9 2 May 2012" /><ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://gawker.com/5902076/snl-explains-the-nudity-in-game-of-thrones |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Toder |first=Matt |title=SNL Explains the Nudity in Game of Thrones |url=http://gawker.com/5902076/snl-explains-the-nudity-in-game-of-thrones |accessdate=2012-05-02 |work=Gawker |date=2012-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在[[权力的游戏_(第三季)|第三季]]中，看到{{le|席恩·葛雷喬伊|Theon Greyjoy}}長期遭受折磨，並最終被[[閹割|閹割]]，該系列也因其使用酷刑而受到批評<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2013/05/-i-game-of-thrones-i-worst-scene-yet/275772/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Orr |first=Christopher |title=Game of Thrones' Worst Scene Yet? |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2013/05/-i-game-of-thrones-i-worst-scene-yet/275772/ |accessdate=2013-05-19 |newspaper=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] |date=2013-05-13 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[紐約_(雜誌)|紐約雜誌]]》稱該場景為「酷刑色情」<ref>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://nymag.com/thecut/2014/05/game-of-thrones-couple-of-the-week-episode-6.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://nymag.com/thecut/2014/05/game-of-thrones-couple-of-the-week-episode-6.html |title=''Game of Thrones'' Couple of the Week: Tyrion and Shae Are Never Getting Back Together |first=Allison P. |last=David |work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]] |date=2014-05-12 |accessdate=2015-07-17 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{le|耶洗別|Jezebel (website)}}》的馬德琳·戴維斯（Madeleine Davies）表示同意，並說：「《權力遊戲》被指責為酷刑色情片並不少見—結合著毫無意義[[物化|物化]]的暴力，有著毫無意義的客體性意象。」根據戴維斯的說法，儘管該劇集的暴力傾向具有敘述性的目的，但席恩於《[[权力的游戏_(第三季)|熊與美少女]]》一集裡的酷刑實在過分了<ref>{{cite news |last=Davis |first=Madeleine |title=Game of Boners: This Is Torture Porn |url=http://jezebel.com/game-of-boners-this-is-torture-porn-504821180 |accessdate=2013-05-17 |newspaper=Jezebel |date=2013-05-13 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716061155/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequels-are-we-getting-all-four-1020065 |archivedate=2017-07-16 }}</ref>。

在[[权力的游戏_(第四季)|第四季]]的第三集《[[权力的游戏_(第四季)#集數列表|破鐐之人]]》中的強姦場景，當中{{le|傑米·蘭尼斯特|Jaime Lannister}}強姦了自己的姐姐兼情人{{le|瑟曦·蘭尼斯特|Cersei Lannister}}，引發了該系列針對婦女性暴力描寫的廣泛公眾討論。據《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的戴夫·伊茲科夫（Dave Itzkoff）稱，該場景引起了公憤，部分原因是導演{{le|阿歷克斯·格雷夫斯|Alex Graves}}評論指，這一場景「最終得到了共識」。伊茲科夫還寫道，劇評人擔心「強姦在電視劇中變得如此普遍，以至於幾乎是背景噪音：一個例行且令人毫不震驚的事」<ref name="New York Times May 2, 2014">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/03/arts/television/for-game-of-thrones-rising-unease-over-rapes-recurring-role.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Itzkoff |first=Dave |title=For 'Game of Thrones,' Rising Unease Over Rape's Recurring Role |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/03/arts/television/for-game-of-thrones-rising-unease-over-rapes-recurring-role.html |accessdate=2014-05-04 |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2014-05-02 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》的索尼亞·薩拉亞（Sonia Saraiya）寫道，該系列選擇刻畫這種性行為，在第一季中的[[丹妮莉絲·坦格利安|丹妮莉絲·坦格利安]]與{{le|卡爾·德羅戈|Khal Drogo}}之間有一個相似之處—兩者在原著小說中都被描述為同意—因為強姦似乎是「剝削有用的東西使人感到驚訝和沮喪」的行為<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.avclub.com/article/rape-thrones-203499 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Saraiya |first=Sonia |title=Rape of Thrones Why are the Game Of Thrones showrunners rewriting the books into misogyny? |url=https://avclub.com/article/rape-thrones-203499 |accessdate=2014-04-21 |newspaper=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]] |date=2014-04-20 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[权力的游戏_(第五季)|第五季]]的《[[权力的游戏_(第五季)|不屈，不撓，不破]]》的一集裡，{{le|珊莎·史塔克|Sansa Stark}}遭{{le|拉姆賽·博爾頓|Ramsay Bolton}}強姦了。大部分評論者，包括《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利場]]》、《沙龍》、《大西洋》和《每日野獸》中的那些劇評人，他們都發現該場景是不必要和藝術上沒有理由的<ref name="Atlantic" /><ref>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728222832/http://www.salon.com/2015/05/18/heres_why_people_are_so_upset_about_the_latest_game_of_thrones_rape_so_cheap_such_an_obvious_choice_i_felt_offended_as_a_fan/ |archivedate=2016-07-28 |url=http://www.salon.com/2015/05/18/heres_why_people_are_so_upset_about_the_latest_game_of_thrones_rape_so_cheap_such_an_obvious_choice_i_felt_offended_as_a_fan/ |title=Here's why people are so upset about the latest "Game of Thrones" rape: "So cheap, such an obvious choice, I felt offended as a fan" |last=Silman |first=Anna |work=[[Salon_(magazine)|Salon]] |date=2015-05-18 |accessdate=2015-06-26 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Telegraph>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513115940/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/game-of-thrones/11608928/Game-of-Thrones-Unbowed-Unbent-Unbroken-season-5-episode-6-review.html |archivedate=2016-05-13 |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/game-of-thrones/11608928/Game-of-Thrones-Unbowed-Unbent-Unbroken-season-5-episode-6-review.html |title=Game of Thrones: Unbowed, Unbent, Unbroken, season 5 episode 6, review: 'raw emotion' |last=Runcie |first=Charlotte |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2015-05-17 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=DailyBeast>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/05/19/the-rape-of-sansa-stark-game-of-thrones-goes-off-book-and-enrages-its-female-fans.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/05/19/the-rape-of-sansa-stark-game-of-thrones-goes-off-book-and-enrages-its-female-fans.html |title=The Rape of Sansa Stark: 'Game of Thrones' Goes Off-Book and Enrages Its Female Fans |last=Leon |first=Melissa |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Beast|The Daily Beast]] |date=2015-05-19 |accessdate=2015-05-20 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。例如，替《名利場》寫作的喬安娜·羅賓遜（Joanna Robinson），說該場景「削弱了珊莎自前季末段以來一直在增長的所有代言<ref>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/05/game-of-thrones-rape-sansa-stark |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/05/game-of-thrones-rape-sansa-stark |title=''Game of Thrones'' Absolutely Did ''Not'' Need to Go There with Sansa Stark |work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]] |first=Joanna |last=Robinson |date=2015-05-17 |accessdate=2015-05-18 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。」相比之下，《[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]》的莎拉·史超域（Sara Stewart）想知道為何觀眾對經歷過類似或更差處理的許多背景角色和小角色沒有同樣的反感<ref name=NYPost>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://nypost.com/2015/05/19/its-a-stark-reality-outrage-over-sansa-rape-scene-misses-the-point/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://nypost.com/2015/05/19/its-a-stark-reality-outrage-over-sansa-rape-scene-misses-the-point/ |title=It's a Stark reality: Outrage over Sansa rape scene misses the point |last=Stewart |first=Sara |work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]] |date=2015-05-19 |accessdate=2015-05-19 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。針對這一情況，流行文化網站《{{le|瑪莉·蘇|Dan Abrams#The Mary Sue}}》宣布將停止對該系列的報導，因為其一再使用強姦作為情節的設置<ref name=TheMarySueIsSoDone>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.themarysue.com/we-will-no-longer-be-promoting-hbos-game-of-thrones/ |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=http://www.themarysue.com/we-will-no-longer-be-promoting-hbos-game-of-thrones/ |title=We Will No Longer Be Promoting HBO's Game of Thrones |last=Pantozzi |first=Jill |website=[[The_Mary_Sue|The Mary Sue]] |date=2015-05-18 |accessdate=2015-05-20 |dead-url=no}}</ref>，而美國參議員[[克蕾兒·麥卡斯基|克蕾兒·麥卡斯基]]說她不會再看該劇了<ref>{{cite news|last=Cillizza|first=Chris|title=Claire McCaskill is done with 'Game of Thrones' after Sunday's rape scene. She's got a point.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/05/19/claire-mccaskill-is-done-with-game-of-thrones-after-sundays-rape-scene-shes-got-a-point/|accessdate=2017-08-09|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2015-05-19|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724150232/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/05/19/claire-mccaskill-is-done-with-game-of-thrones-after-sundays-rape-scene-shes-got-a-point/|archivedate=2017-07-24}}</ref>。

在第六、七季中看到丹妮莉絲、珊莎和瑟曦擔任統治職位時，《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的艾莉莎·羅森伯格（Alyssa Rosenberg）指出，該系列片段可以被視為「被殘酷對待和強姦的女性獲得權力時會發生何事復仇幻想的長故事」—就是說，她們的過去使她們變得無能為力，但要輪流作出殘酷的行為，而她們的個人解放不會影響需要保護他人免受痛苦的社會變遷<ref>{{cite news|last=Rosenberg|first=Alyssa|title=The arguments about women and power in 'Game of Thrones' have never been more unsettling|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/act-four/wp/2017/08/09/the-arguments-about-women-and-power-in-game-of-thrones-have-never-been-more-unsettling/|accessdate=2017-08-09|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2017-08-09|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809212138/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/act-four/wp/2017/08/09/the-arguments-about-women-and-power-in-game-of-thrones-have-never-been-more-unsettling/|archivedate=2017-08-09}}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》在第七季之前報導指：「即使貝尼奧夫和魏斯並不總是承認這一點，該劇集還是發生了變化。場景在一個或其他妓院中進行闡述，例如已被刪減了的那些<ref name="daddario2017">{{Cite magazine |last=D'Addadio |first=Daniel |date=2017-07-10 |title='Game of Thrones': Inside the World's Most Popular Show |url=http://time.com/game-of-thrones-2017/ |magazine=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |access-date=2017-09-02 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405173744/http://time.com/game-of-thrones-2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

