自該系列第6季以來，在較暗的場景燈光或光線不足一直是批評的焦點<ref>{{cite news |date=2019-04-29 |last=Flint |first=Hanna |title=This is why the lighting is so bad in 'Game of Thrones' |url=https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/lighting-bad-game-thrones-124901278.html |work=Yahoo |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="Every week, social media is filled with complaints about how dark the scenes looks and more importantly how it affects their ability to see the action." |archive-date=2019-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504031831/https://uk.movies.yahoo.com/lighting-bad-game-thrones-124901278.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=2016-09-09 |last=Lallo |first=Michael |title=Will someone please turn on the lights: Why have TV dramas literally become so dark? |url=https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/tv-and-radio/will-someone-please-turn-on-the-lights-why-have-tv-dramas-literally-become-so-dark-20160909-grchcu.html |work=The Sydney Morning Herald |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="To many fans, Game of Thrones is too dark. Not figuratively – they literally can't perceive what's happening on screen." |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430032342/https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/tv-and-radio/will-someone-please-turn-on-the-lights-why-have-tv-dramas-literally-become-so-dark-20160909-grchcu.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=2019-04-17 |last=Sharf |first=Zack |title=Does 'Game of Thrones' Have an 'Ozark' Problem? Season 8 Is So Dark It's Hard to See |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/04/game-of-thrones-too-dark-fans-cant-see-1202059546/ |work=IndieWire |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="Fear's jokey comment encapsulated one of the biggest fan criticisms about the "Game of Thrones" premiere: The show is so visually dark that viewers can't even see what's happening on screen. Many fans took to social media during the episode to complain about the color palette, with some wondering if it was their TV brightness setting that was the issue." |archive-date=2020-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224154626/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/04/game-of-thrones-too-dark-fans-cant-see-1202059546/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Warner |first=Sam |date=2019-04-16 |title=Game of Thrones viewers have one big complaint about season 8, episode 1 |url=https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/a27159387/game-of-thrones-viewers-complain-season-8-episode-1-too-dark/ |work=Digital Spy |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="Yep, many complained that parts of the episode were too dark – and we don't mean just twisted dark after seeing the Night King's artistic flair." |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430032451/https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/ustv/a27159387/game-of-thrones-viewers-complain-season-8-episode-1-too-dark/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2016年，《{{le|喧囂雜誌|Bustle (magazine)}}》的凱特琳·卡拉格里（Caitlyn Callegari）列舉了31個場景示例，當中包括觀眾從無法分辨角色們的頭髮顏色，以至他們無法看到正在發生事情的燈光問題<ref>{{cite news |date=2016-05-29 |last=Callegari |first=Caitlyn |title=31 Times 'Game of Thrones' Needed To Lighten Up, Literally |url=https://www.bustle.com/articles/160916-31-times-game-of-thrones-needed-to-lighten-up-literally |work=Bustle |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="Game of Thrones needs to turn on the lights, or else I am sending them my ophthalmologist bill. For real, GoT powers that be, it's super hard to squint for a straight hour every week because your episodes are so freakin' dark." |archive-date=2020-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611014146/https://www.bustle.com/articles/160916-31-times-game-of-thrones-needed-to-lighten-up-literally |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一些評論者注意到，這是由具有主要拍攝電影經驗的人們製作的節目有著更廣泛趨勢的一部分<ref>{{cite news |date=2016-06-29 |last=Dessem |first=Matthew |title=Why TV Shows Are Darker Than They've Ever Been |url=https://slate.com/culture/2016/06/cinematographers-from-game-of-thrones-jessica-jones-and-better-call-saul-on-why-tv-shows-are-darker-than-theyve-ever-been.html |work=Slate |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="Watching Game of Thrones this season, you may have asked yourself: Is something wrong with my television? Surely there is some other setting that would brighten up the inside of Bran Stark's cave, or heighten the contrast between Cersei Lannister's robes and the shadowy chambers of her prison cell. But no, that's just the way the show is supposed to look. And Game of Thrones is not alone: HBO has made a cottage industry of dimly-lit hourlong dramas" |archive-date=2020-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408195637/https://slate.com/culture/2016/06/cinematographers-from-game-of-thrones-jessica-jones-and-better-call-saul-on-why-tv-shows-are-darker-than-theyve-ever-been.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，暗示他們「沒有掌握以電視為媒介的細微差別（或缺少）」特別是在電視屏幕上與電影院的大屏幕上觀看場景之間的區別<ref>{{cite news |date=2016-03-19 |last=Burgess |first=Genevieve |title=Why is TV, Literally, So Dark? |url=http://www.pajiba.com/think_pieces/why-is-tv-literally-so-dark.php |work=Pajiba |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="A lot of these shows are also made by people who have experience working primarily on films, and film aesthetic has always been visually darker than TV. Because films are meant to be watched on very large screens in very dark rooms, while most TV is watched on smaller screens in brightly lit rooms. It seems the people making these shows aren't evaluating the lighting for the proper venue." |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626191747/http://www.pajiba.com/think_pieces/why-is-tv-literally-so-dark.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2017年的一次訪問中，從事該劇集的攝影師{{le|羅拔·麥克拉克倫|Robert McLachlan (cinematographer)}}，他解釋指缺乏照明是一種藝術性選擇：「我們正在努力變得盡量寫實」<ref>{{cite news |last=Renfro |first=Kim |date=2017-08-19 |title='Game of Thrones' cinematographer reveals the unexpected perils of filming: 'They were going to pull us all off the cliff' |url=https://www.thisisinsider.com/game-of-thrones-cinematographer-interview-season-7-kit-kite-2017-8 |work=Insider |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="I think we're all very much on the same page where we're trying to be as naturalistic as possible. We want to make these sets and locations feel as if they're absolutely not lit by us, but only by mother nature or some candles..." |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430033858/https://www.thisisinsider.com/game-of-thrones-cinematographer-interview-season-7-kit-kite-2017-8 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Paine |first=Hannah |date=2019-04-29 |title=Game of Thrones fans fume over 'too dark' episode |url=https://www.news.com.au/entertainment/tv/game-of-thrones/game-of-thrones-fans-fume-over-too-dark-episode/news-story/755afb0a00f0d59c7100028debc4737a |work=news.com.au |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="It's not the first time Game of Thrones has come under fire for its shots being too dark, however. According to one of the show's cinematographers, it's a very deliberate choice." |archive-date=2019-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429055910/https://www.news.com.au/entertainment/tv/game-of-thrones/game-of-thrones-fans-fume-over-too-dark-episode/news-story/755afb0a00f0d59c7100028debc4737a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[权力的游戏_(第八季)|第八季]]的第三集《{{le|漫漫長夜|The Long Night (Game of Thrones)}}》中，其批評達到了高潮<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/news/game-of-thrones-battle-is-biggest-ever-but-it-was-way-too-dark/ |title=Game of Thrones battle was the biggest ever, but way too dark to see |work=CNET |first=Mark |last=Serrels |date=2019-04-28 |accessdate=2019-05-07 |archive-date=2020-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515012200/https://www.cnet.com/news/game-of-thrones-battle-is-biggest-ever-but-it-was-way-too-dark/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/game-of-thrones-too-dark-lighting-battle-of-winterfell |title='Game of Thrones' fans complain about 'too dark' lighting in Battle of Winterfell |work=Fox News |first=Katherine |last=Lam |date=2019-04-29 |accessdate=2019-05-07 |archive-date=2020-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520075936/https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/game-of-thrones-too-dark-lighting-battle-of-winterfell |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在短短不到幾分鐘的時間內，觀眾進入到Twitter之類的社交媒體網站，表達了他們對於觀看這場戰鬥中遇到嚴重困難的事實，並試圖弄清楚究竟發生了甚麼事<ref>{{cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/2019/04/29/game-of-thrones-season-8-episode-3-too-dark-fans-furious/ |title=Game of Thrones Fans Are Furious the Winterfell Battle Scenes Are Too Dark |work=Comicbook.com |first=Nicole |last=Drum |date=2019-04-28 |accessdate=2019-05-07 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813082529/https://comicbook.com/tv-shows/2019/04/29/game-of-thrones-season-8-episode-3-too-dark-fans-furious/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/game-of-thrones-dark-battle-of-winterfell-cinematography-1203199892/ |title='Game of Thrones' Fans Complain About Battle of Winterfell's Dark Cinematography |work=Variety |first=Erin |last=Nyren |date=2019-04-28 |accessdate=2019-05-07 |archive-date=2019-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929231457/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/game-of-thrones-dark-battle-of-winterfell-cinematography-1203199892/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/tv/0/lighten-jon-snow-game-thrones-dark/ |title=Lighten up, Jon Snow: why is Game of Thrones so ridiculously dark? |work=The Daily Telegraph |first=Sam |last=Parker |date=2019-04-30 |accessdate=2019-05-07 |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430032249/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/tv/0/lighten-jon-snow-game-thrones-dark/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Dessem |first=Matthew |date=2019-04-29 |title=Why You Couldn't See a Damn Thing on This Week's Game of Thrones |url=https://slate.com/culture/2019/04/game-of-thrones-long-night-dark-cinematography-twitter-complaints.html |work=Slate |accessdate=2019-05-07 |quote="On Sunday night, Twitter was full of viewers complaining about the show's cinematography, which has often been dark, but never quite so consistently stygian." |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414183511/https://slate.com/culture/2019/04/game-of-thrones-long-night-dark-cinematography-twitter-complaints.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

