《冰與火之歌》和《權力遊戲》擁有廣泛而活躍的國際[[粉絲文化|粉絲群]]。《[[紐約_(雜誌)|紐約雜誌]]》於2012年的流行文化中把該系列的粉絲列為最忠實的粉絲，比較[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]、[[賈斯汀·比伯|賈斯汀·比伯]]、[[哈利·波特|哈利波特]]和[[星球大戰|星球大戰]]的粉絲還要多<ref name="Vulture October 15, 2012">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.vulture.com/2012/10/25-most-devoted-fans.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |title=The 25 Most Devoted Fan Bases |url=https://vulture.com/2012/10/25-most-devoted-fans.html |accessdate=2012-10-17 |newspaper=[[Vulture.com|Vulture]] |date=2012-10-15 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。其粉絲包括多位政治領袖，如：美國前總統[[贝拉克·奥巴马|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/30/us/obamas-tv-picks-anything-edgy-with-hints-of-reality.html |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=Shear |first=Michael |title=Obama's TV Picks |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/30/us/obamas-tv-picks-anything-edgy-with-hints-of-reality.html |accessdate=2013-12-29 |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2013-12-29 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105010138/http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2013/12/obama-favorite-tv-shows-game-of-thrones |archivedate=2014-01-05 |last=Ghahremani |first=Tanya |title=President Obama 'Really Likes' Game of Thrones, In Case You Were Wondering |url=http://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2013/12/obama-favorite-tv-shows-game-of-thrones |accessdate=2013-12-30 |work=[[Complex_(magazine)|Complex]] |date=2013-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、英國前首相[[大衛·卡梅倫|大衛·卡梅倫]]<ref>{{cite web |title=David Cameron admits he is a 'Throney' and 'huge fan' on Game of Thrones studio tour |url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/politics/568919/David-Cameron-Game-of-Thrones-General-Election-2015 |work=[[Daily_Express|Daily Express]] |first=Victoria |last=Armstrong |date=2015-04-07 |accessdate=2015-04-10 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716061155/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequels-are-we-getting-all-four-1020065 |archivedate=2017-07-16 }}</ref>、澳洲前總理[[朱莉亞·吉拉德|朱莉亞·吉拉德]]<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130716014754/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/may/26/julia-gillard-game-of-thrones |archivedate=2013-07-16 |last=Taylor |first=Lenore |title=Julia Gillard reveals Game of Thrones addiction |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/may/26/julia-gillard-game-of-thrones |accessdate=2013-05-30 |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2013-05-30 |location=London |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426145920/http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/apr/07/game-of-thrones-parallels-prime-minister |archivedate=2016-04-26 |last=Gillard |first=Julia |title=Game of Thrones has parallels with my time as Australian prime minister |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2014/apr/07/game-of-thrones-parallels-prime-minister? |accessdate=2014-04-07 |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2014-04-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，及荷蘭外交大臣{{le|弗朗斯·添默文斯|Frans Timmermans}}，他在2013年的演講中引用了馬田小說中的名言來映襯歐洲政治<ref>{{cite news |last=Luoma |first=Sarah |title=Dutch foreign minister uses 'Game of Thrones' as political analogy |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/fun/game-of-thrones/news/a486020/dutch-foreign-minister-uses-game-of-thrones-as-political-analogy/ |accessdate=2016-11-02 |work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |date=2013-05-31 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20161217132623/http://www.digitalspy.com/fun/game-of-thrones/news/a486020/dutch-foreign-minister-uses-game-of-thrones-as-political-analogy/ |archivedate=2016-12-17 }}</ref>。

[[英國廣播公司新聞|英國廣播公司新聞]]於2013年表示「粉絲們的熱情和奉獻精神」創造了一種跟其他受歡迎電視劇集不同的現象，並在[[同人小說|粉絲小說]]中得以體現出來<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903190051/http://www.salon.com/2013/06/16/the_best_and_the_weirdest_of_game_of_thrones_fanfiction/ |archivedate=2016-09-03 |last=Templeton |first=Molly |title=The best (and the weirdest) of "Game of Thrones" fanfiction |url=http://www.salon.com/2013/06/16/the_best_and_the_weirdest_of_game_of_thrones_fanfiction/ |accessdate=2013-07-06 |newspaper=[[Salon_(magazine)|Salon]] |date=2013-06-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以《權力遊戲》為主題的詼諧模仿套路，和父母們會以該系列的角色來為孩子命名；引用的作者將這成功歸功於該系列劇集和小說的史詩規模、豐富細節、道德上的歧義、直言不諱的性事<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-21856915 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |last=de Castella |first=Tom |title=Game of Thrones: Why does it inspire such devotion among fans? |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-21856915 |accessdate=2013-03-23 |newspaper=[[BBC_News_Magazine|BBC News Magazine]] |date=2013-03-22 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。前一年，「{{le|艾莉雅|Arya (name)}}」這個女孩名字的人氣從711位躍升至413位，是美國上升最快的女孩名字<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019200832/http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/05/10/arya-game-of-thrones-baby-names/ |archivedate=2014-10-19 |last=Carlson |first=Adam |title='Game of Thrones' domination is nearly complete: 'Arya' is the fastest-rising name for baby girls |url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/05/10/arya-game-of-thrones-baby-names/ |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2013-05-10 |accessdate=2013-05-10 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

