=== 獎項 ===
{{main|{{le|《權力遊戲》所獲獎項及提名|List of awards and nominations received by Game of Thrones}}}}
自《權力遊戲》系列首播以來，它已經贏得無數獎項，包括58項《[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]》、《[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]》5次及《[[皮博迪獎|皮博迪獎]]》；它保持著贏得最多《艾美獎》劇本獎項記錄的一部電視劇，超越自2004年《[[歡樂一家親|費氏話你知]]》37勝的記錄，並獲得最多戲劇提名達161項<ref name="emmys.com"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://time.com/4498870/emmys-2016-game-of-thrones-most-wins/ |title=Game of Thrones Now Has the Most Emmy Wins Ever |first=Eliana |last=Dockterman |date=2016-09-18 |work=Time |accessdate=2016-09-19 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919042453/http://time.com/4498870/emmys-2016-game-of-thrones-most-wins/ |archivedate=2016-09-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601004713/http://www.peabody.uga.edu/71stwinners.php |archivedate=2012-06-01 |title=Complete List of Recipients of the 71st Annual Peabody Awards |url=http://www.peabody.uga.edu/71stwinners.php |publisher=Peabody Awards |date=2012-04-04 |accessdate=2016-11-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=2019 EMMY NOMINATION SNUBS & SURPRISES: GAME OF THRONES MAKES HISTORY, SCHITT'S CREEK POPS |url=https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/2019-emmy-nomination-snubs-surprises-game-of-thrones-schitts-creek-netflix/ |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |date=2019-07-16 |accessdate=2019-07-17 |archive-date=2019-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205111623/https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/2019-emmy-nomination-snubs-surprises-game-of-thrones-schitts-creek-netflix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2011年，[[权力的游戏_(第一季)|第一季]]獲得13項艾美獎提名（包括{{le|傑出系列劇集|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Drama Series}}），並獲得{{le|劇集系列最佳男配角獎|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actor in a Drama Series}}（由[[彼特·丁拉基|彼特·丁拉基]]飾演的{{le|提利昂·蘭尼斯特|Tyrion Lannister}}獲得），以及{{le|傑出主題設計|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Main Title Design}}。其他提名還包括{{le|傑出導演|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series}}（[[凜冬將至|凜冬將至]]）及{{le|傑出劇集系列劇本|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Writing for a Drama Series}}（{{le|貝勒聖堂|Baelor}}）<ref name="emmys.com"/>。丁拉基還曾在《{{le|金球獎|Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor – Series, Miniseries or Television Film}}》、《{{le|衛星獎|Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actor – Series, Miniseries or Television Film}}》及《[[尖叫獎|尖叫獎]]》中奪得「系列，迷你劇或電視電影最佳男配角獎」<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821120407/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-globes-2012-winners-list-282032 |archivedate=2016-08-21 |url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-globes-2012-winners-list-282032 |title=Golden Globes 2012: The Winners List |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2012-01-15 |accessdate=2016-08-29 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829120407/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/2011-Scream-Awards-Winners-Vampires-Wizards-Swans-27353.html |archivedate=2012-08-29 |url=https://cinemablend.com/new/2011-Scream-Awards-Winners-Vampires-Wizards-Swans-27353.html |title=The 2011 Scream Awards Winners: Vampires, Wizards And Swans |publisher=Cinemablend |first=Kelly |last=West |date=2011-06-19 |accessdate=2016-08-29 |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318221149/http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2011/ |archivedate=2016-03-18 |url=http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2011/ |title=2011 Winners |publisher=[[International_Press_Academy|International Press Academy]] |date=2011-06-19 |accessdate=2016-08-29 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年，[[权力的游戏_(第二季)|第二季]]從《[[第64屆黃金時段艾美獎|第64屆黃金時段艾美獎]]》的11項提名中獲得六個獎項，包括「傑出劇集系列」及「劇集系列最佳男配角（丁拉基）」<ref name="emmys.com"/>。

2013年，[[权力的游戏_(第三季)|第三季]]獲得了16項《艾美獎》提名，當中包括「傑出劇集系列」、「劇集系列最佳男配角（丁拉基）」、「{{le|劇集系列最佳女配角|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series}}（[[艾美莉·克拉克|艾美莉·克拉克]]）」、「{{le|劇集系列最佳客串女演員|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actress in a Drama Series}}（[[戴安娜·瑞格|戴安娜·瑞格]]）」及傑出作品（《[[卡斯特梅的雨季|卡斯特梅的雨季]]》），最終贏得兩項{{le|創意藝術艾美獎|65th Primetime Creative Arts Emmy Awards}}<ref name="emmys.com"/>；同年，《[[美國編劇工會|美國編劇工會]]》把《權力遊戲》列為電視史上第40位「最佳寫作」的電視劇集<ref>{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2013/06/wgas-101-best-written-tv-series-of-all-time-complete-list/ |title='101 Best Written TV Series Of All Time' From WGA/TV Guide: Complete List |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2013-06-02 |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6H5yn3sZq?url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/wgas-101-best-written-tv-series-of-all-time-complete-list/ |archivedate=2013-06-03 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，[[权力的游戏_(第四季)|第四季]]從《[[第66屆黃金時段艾美獎|第66屆黃金時段艾美獎]]》的19項提名，包括「傑出劇集系列」、「劇集系列最佳男配角（丁拉基）」、「劇集系列最佳女配角（[[琳娜·海蒂|蓮娜·赫迪]]）」、「劇集系列最佳客串女演員（瑞格）」、「傑出導演（[[权力的游戏_(第四季)#集數列表|長城守望者]]）」及「傑出作品（[[权力的游戏_(第四季)#集數列表|萬生之子]]）」，結果中獲得四個獎項<ref name="emmys.com"/>。

2015年，[[权力的游戏_(第五季)|第五季]]的劇集於一年內贏得最多的《黃金時段艾美獎》，包括「傑出劇集系列」在內24項提名中的12個獎項；其他勝出獎項包括：「劇集系列最佳男配角（丁拉基）」、「傑出導演（[[权力的游戏_(第五季)#集數|聖母憐憫]]）」和「傑出劇本（聖母憐憫）」，以及八項{{le|黃金時段艾美獎創意藝術獎|67th Primetime Creative Arts Emmy Awards}}<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901192112/http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/game-of-thrones-emmy-wins-record-1201598356/ |archivedate=2016-09-01 |url=https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/game-of-thrones-emmy-wins-record-1201598356/ |title='Game of Thrones' Sets Record for Most Emmy Wins in a Year |first=Laura |last=Prudom |date=2015-09-20 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate=2015-09-21 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，該劇於《[[荷里活報道|荷李活報道]]》的「有史以來最佳的電視節目」列表中排名第四<ref>{{cite news |url=https://hollywoodreporter.com/lists/best-tv-shows-ever-top-819499/item/x-files-hollywoods-100-favorite-821363 |title=Hollywood's 100 Favorite TV Shows |accessdate=2016-11-05 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105223813/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/best-tv-shows-ever-top-819499/item/x-files-hollywoods-100-favorite-821363 |archivedate=2016-11-05}}</ref>；該劇於2016年《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》的「有史以來最好的50齣電視節目」中排名第七位<ref>{{cite news |url=https://empireonline.com/movies/features/best-tv-shows-ever/ |title=The 50 Greatest TV Shows of All Time |accessdate=2016-11-05 |work=[[Empire_(film_magazine)|Empire]] |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104130445/http://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/best-tv-shows-ever/ |archivedate=2016-11-04}}</ref>；同年，《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石雜誌]]》將其命名為「有史以來最偉大的電視節目」的第12位<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/tv/lists/100-greatest-tv-shows-of-all-time-w439520/late-night-with-david-letterman-w439627 |title=100 Greatest TV Shows of All Time |accessdate=2016-11-05 |work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105224622/http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/lists/100-greatest-tv-shows-of-all-time-w439520/late-night-with-david-letterman-w439627 |archivedate=2016-11-05}}</ref>。2019年，英國《[[衛報|衛報]]》將其排在[[21世紀|21世紀]]最偉大的100部電視劇集名單第七名<ref name=Guardian_20190926>{{cite news |title= The 100 best TV shows of the 21st century |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/sep/16/100-best-tv-shows-of-the-21st-century |work=The Guardian |date=2019-09-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101054025/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/sep/16/100-best-tv-shows-of-the-21st-century |archivedate=2019-11-01|language=en-GB }}</ref>。

2016年，[[权力的游戏_(第六季)|第六季]]得到《[[第68屆黃金時段艾美獎|第68屆黃金時段艾美獎]]》的最多提名（23項），它贏得「傑出劇集系列」、「傑出導演（[[权力的游戏_(第六季)#分集剧情|私生子戰役]]）」、「傑出作品（私生子戰役）」及九項{{le|黃金時段艾美獎創意藝術獎|68th Primetime Creative Arts Emmy Awards}}。提名包括「劇集系列最佳男配角（丁拉基與[[基特·哈靈頓|傑·夏寧頓]]）」、「劇集系列最佳女配角（克拉克、海蒂及[[麦茜·威廉姆斯|梅西·威廉斯]]）、「{{le|劇集系列最佳客串男演員|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Drama Series}}（[[麥斯·馮·西度|麥斯·馮·西度]]）」及「傑出導演（[[权力的游戏_(第五季)#集數|門]]）」<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830110843/http://variety.com/2016/tv/awards/game-of-thrones-2016-emmys-nominations-1201814023/ |archivedate=2016-08-30 |url=https://variety.com/2016/tv/awards/game-of-thrones-2016-emmys-nominations-1201814023/ |title='Game of Thrones' Rules 2016 Emmy Race With 23 Nominations |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Laura |last=Prudom |date=2016-07-14 |accessdate=2016-07-14 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[权力的游戏_(第七季)|第七季]]於2018年的《[[第70屆黃金時段艾美獎|第70屆黃金時段艾美獎]]》獲得最多提名（22項<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/awards/game-of-thrones-saturday-night-live-westworld-emmy-nominees-1202871447/ |title='Game of Thrones,' Netflix Lead Emmy Nominees |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2018-07-12 |accessdate=2018-07-12 |archive-date=2019-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923014146/https://variety.com/2018/tv/awards/game-of-thrones-saturday-night-live-westworld-emmy-nominees-1202871447/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>），它最終獲得「傑出劇集系列」、「劇集系列最佳男配角（丁拉基）」及七項{{le|黃金時段艾美獎創意藝術獎|70th Primetime Creative Arts Emmy Awards}}<ref>{{cite news |url=https://tvline.com/2018/09/17/emmys-2018-awards-winners-list/ |title=Emmys: Mrs. Maisel, Versace, Barry and Game of Thrones Among Big Winners |work=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |first=Matt Webb |last=Mitovich |date=2018-09-17 |accessdate=2018-09-18 |archive-date=2019-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019110409/https://tvline.com/2018/09/17/emmys-2018-awards-winners-list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。提名包括「劇集系列最佳女配角（赫迪）」、「劇集系列最佳男配角（[[尼可拉·科斯特-瓦爾道|尼古拉·高斯達-華竇]]）」、「{{le|劇集系列最佳客串女演員|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actress in a Drama Series}}（瑞格）」、「傑出劇本（[[大衛·貝尼奧夫|大衛·貝尼奧夫]]與[[D·B·魏斯|D·B·魏斯]]的《[[权力的游戏_(第七季)|龍與狼]]》）」及「傑出劇集系列導演（{{le|傑里米·波德斯瓦|Jeremy Podeswa}}的《龍與狼》和[[亞倫·泰勒_(導演)|亞倫·泰勒]]的[[权力的游戏_(第七季)#集數列表|長城之外]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2018-emmy-nominations-list-see-all-the-nominees-1110785/item/writing-a-comedy-series-emmy-nominations-2018-1110796 |title=Emmys: Netflix Beats HBO With Most Nominations |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2018-07-12 |accessdate=2018-07-12 |archive-date=2018-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713011538/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/2018-emmy-nominations-list-see-all-the-nominees-1110785/item/writing-a-comedy-series-emmy-nominations-2018-1110796 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年，[[权力的游戏_(第八季)|最後一季]]的劇集打破了《{{le|紐約重案組|NYPD Blue}}》於1994年{{le|第46屆黃金時段艾美獎|46th Primetime Emmy Awards}}長達25年的記錄，該劇的首季於當年得到了26項的提名，《權力遊戲》創下了32項任何常規系列獲得艾美獎提名的最高紀錄，成為同年獲得最多《艾美獎》提名的新紀錄<ref>{{cite news |last1=Chitwood |first1=Adam |title=Emmy Nominations 2019: 'Game of Thrones' Breaks 'NYPD Blue' Record with 32 Nominations |url=https://collider.com/emmy-nominations-2019-explained/ |accessdate=2019-06-01 |work=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]] |date=2019-07-16 |language=en |archive-date=2019-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722020640/http://collider.com/emmy-nominations-2019-explained/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Emmy 2019: Game of Thrones breaks 'NYPD Blue' record with 32 nominations |url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/game-of-thrones-breaks-record-with-32-emmy-nominations-119071700032_1.html |accessdate=2019-07-17 |work=[[Business_Standard|Business Standard]] |date=2019-07-16 |language=en |archive-date=2019-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729035542/https://www.business-standard.com/article/pti-stories/game-of-thrones-breaks-record-with-32-emmy-nominations-119071700032_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這些提名包括「傑出劇集系列」、「傑出系列劇本」，以及10項的演出提名。[[艾美莉·克拉克|艾美莉·克拉克]]與[[基特·哈靈頓|傑·夏寧頓]]位列主演類別；而[[阿爾菲·阿倫|阿爾菲·阿倫]]、彼得·丁拉基、尼古拉·高斯達-華竇、[[關朵琳·克莉絲蒂|關朵琳·克莉絲蒂]]、蓮娜·赫迪、[[蘇菲·特納|蘇菲·特納]]及梅西·威廉斯都在配角類別；而[[卡里斯·范·豪滕|卡莉絲·范·荷登]]則在客串演出類別<ref>{{cite news |last1=Travers |first1=Ben |title=2019 Emmy Predictions: The 71st Annual Primetime Emmys Are Gonna be Wild |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/2019-emmy-predictions-71-primetime-emmys-nominations-winners-1202048893/ |accessdate=2019-06-01 |work=IndieWire |date=2019-03-06 |language=en |archive-date=2019-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531222250/https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/2019-emmy-predictions-71-primetime-emmys-nominations-winners-1202048893/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該系列最終獲得了12個獎項，成為首個贏得該獎的八季劇集系列，並憑其紀錄（以前是在5季中實現）於單一季度中贏得大部分艾美獎。同時，它也追平了最多「最傑出劇集系列」獲勝的紀錄，成為繼《{{le|五個一夜情|Hill Street Blues}}》、《[[洛城法網|洛城法網]]》、《[[白宫群英|白宫群英]]》及《[[广告狂人|廣告狂人]]》後獲得四連勝的第五個劇集系列；不像所有其他記錄保持者在首四個季度都勝出，《權力遊戲》在最尾的四個季度裡創下了紀錄<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ew.com/emmys/2019/09/22/game-of-thrones-best-drama-emmy-season-8/ |title=Game of Thrones wins best drama Emmy for season 8, ties record |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=2019-09-22 |accessdate=2019-09-24 |archive-date=2020-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403010331/https://ew.com/emmys/2019/09/22/game-of-thrones-best-drama-emmy-season-8/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/game-of-thrones-most-emmys-won-series-single-season-record-emmy-awards/ |title='Game of Thrones' Ties Its Own Record for Most Emmys Won by a Series in a Single Season |work=[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]] |first=Jennifer |last=Maas |date=2019-09-22 |accessdate=2019-09-24 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731151038/https://www.thewrap.com/game-of-thrones-most-emmys-won-series-single-season-record-emmy-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。彼特·丁拉基破紀錄憑該系列連續獲得第四個「劇情類劇集最佳男配角」；他的提名也擴大了他類別的最多提名至8個（每個季度中有一個）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2019/09/22/emmys-2019-peter-dinklage-wins-game-of-thrones-new-record/ |title=Peter Dinklage Sets Emmys Record With 4th Supporting Drama Actor Win |work=[[TVLine|TVLine]] |first=Andy |last=Swift |date=2019-09-22 |accessdate=2019-09-24 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207143813/https://tvline.com/2019/09/22/emmys-2019-peter-dinklage-wins-game-of-thrones-new-record/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/awards/peter-dinklage-game-of-thrones-2019-supporting-drama-actor-emmy-1203303698/ |title=Emmys: Peter Dinklage Sets Record With Supporting Actor Win for 'Game of Thrones' |first=Danielle |last=Turchiano |work=Variety |date=2019-09-23 |accessdate=2019-09-23 |archive-date=2020-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107234304/https://variety.com/2019/tv/awards/peter-dinklage-game-of-thrones-2019-supporting-drama-actor-emmy-1203303698/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

