=== 後續劇 ===
{{quote box|bgcolor=#FFFFF0|quote=前傳的系列故事發生在《權力的遊戲》之前數千年，劇集描述了世界從英雄紀元的黃金時代到黑暗時代的蛻變。唯一可以確定的事情是：維斯特洛大陸歷史上那些聳人聽聞的秘密、異鬼的真正起源、東方世界的神秘往事以及史塔克家族的傳奇經歷等等，這些故事並非如同我們認知的那樣。|align=right|width=30%|source= <small>——[[HBO|HBO]]日誌</small><ref name="IGN 180616">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2018/06/16/game-of-thrones-the-age-of-heroes-of-the-spinoff-series-explained |title=Game of Thrones Spinoff: What is The Age of Heroes? |last=Schedeen |first=Jesse |website=IGN |date=2018-06-16|access-date=2018-09-02 |language=en-US |archive-date=2018-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902090050/http://www.ign.com/articles/2018/06/16/game-of-thrones-the-age-of-heroes-of-the-spinoff-series-explained |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}

2017年5月，經過數年的關於《權力遊戲》[[外傳|後續系列]]的諸多猜測後，[[HBO|HBO]]分別委託{{le|麥斯·鮑倫斯坦|Max Borenstein}}、{{le|珍·古德曼|Jane Goldman}}、[[布萊恩·海格蘭|布萊恩·海格蘭]]、{{le|卡莉·雷|Carly Wray}}和布萊恩·科格曼（Bryan Cogman）<ref>{{cite news |url=https://ew.com/tv/2017/09/20/game-thrones-bryan-cogman-5th-prequel/ |title=Game of Thrones writer Bryan Cogman developing a 5th prequel series |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=2017-09-20 |accessdate=2017-09-20 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303164316/https://ew.com/tv/2017/09/20/game-thrones-bryan-cogman-5th-prequel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以發展五部獨立的《權力遊戲》後續系列；所有編劇將分別單獨跟[[喬治·R·R·馬丁|馬田]]合作，後者還聯合寫了兩個劇本<ref>{{cite news |last1=Goldberg |first1=Lesley |title='Game of Thrones': Fifth "Successor Show" in the Works at HBO, George R.R. Martin Says |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-fifth-successor-show-works-at-hbo-george-rr-martin-says-1003682 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2017-05-14 |access-date=2017-05-15|language=en-US |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515142249/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-fifth-successor-show-works-at-hbo-george-rr-martin-says-1003682 |archivedate={{Start date|2017|5|15}}}}</ref>。

2017年9月，有報導稱《權力遊戲》編劇{{le|布萊恩·考克曼|Bryan Cogman}}將負責開發第五部前傳劇集<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ew.com/tv/2017/09/20/game-thrones-bryan-cogman-5th-prequel/ |title=Game of Thrones writer Bryan Cogman developing a 5th prequel series |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=2017-09-20|access-date=2017-09-20 |language=en-US |archive-date=2017-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920195244/http://ew.com/tv/2017/09/20/game-thrones-bryan-cogman-5th-prequel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[D·B·魏斯|D·B·魏斯]]與[[大衛·班尼奧夫|大衛·班尼奧夫]]表示他們將不參與任何衍生劇集的項目<ref name="finalseason">{{cite web |url=http://ew.com/tv/2017/06/02/game-of-thrones-prequel-final-season-interview/ |title=Game of Thrones: HBO clarifies prequels, final seasons plan |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=2017-06-02 |access-date=2017-06-02|language=en-US |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602204015/http://ew.com/tv/2017/06/02/game-of-thrones-prequel-final-season-interview/ |archivedate=2017-06-02}}</ref>，並希望粉絲能夠繼續欣賞該劇的系列。馬田指所有正在討論的概念都是前傳的，儘管他認為稱之為「後續劇」更貼切，因為它們不是《權力遊戲》傳統意義上的衍生物。他排除了羅伯特的叛亂（{{le|羅伯特·巴拉森|Robert Baratheon}}推翻了丹妮莉絲的父親）作為一個可能的想法，並透露有可能是韋斯特羅斯大陸以外的一些故事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://grrm.livejournal.com/536859.html |title=About Those Spinoffs ... |first=George R.R. |last=Martin |date=2017-05-14 |website=Not A Blog|access-date=2017-08-06 |dead-url=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814193454/http://grrm.livejournal.com/536859.html |archivedate=2017-08-14}}</ref>。2018年9月，HBO的節目總監凱西·布洛伊斯（Casey Bloys）表示其中一些想法已被完全拋棄，而其他仍保留作未來可能性<ref name="#1">{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-tca-1202433187/ |title='Game Of Thrones': HBO Boss On Finale Season Premiere, Prequel – TCA |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2018-07-25 |work=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2018-09-02 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303164335/https://deadline.com/2018/07/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-tca-1202433187/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://grrm.livejournal.com/536859.html |title=About Those Spinoffs ...|first=George R.R. |last=Martin |date=2017-05-14 |access-date=2017-08-06|language=en-US |website=Not A Blog |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814193454/http://grrm.livejournal.com/536859.html |archivedate=2017-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-tca-1202433187/ |title='Game Of Thrones': HBO Boss On Finale Season Premiere, Prequel – TCA |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |website=Deadline |date=2018-07-25 |access-date=2018-09-02 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303164335/https://deadline.com/2018/07/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-tca-1202433187/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；馬田說：「其中至少有兩個是紮實基於《{{le|火與血|Fire & Blood (novel)}}》裡的材料<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2018/nov/10/game-of-thrones-george-rr-martin-the-winds-of-winter-interview |title=I've been struggling with it': George RR Martin on The Winds of Winter |work=The Guardian |first=Sian |last=Cain |date=2018-11-10 |accessdate=2019-04-27 |archive-date=2020-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521171251/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2018/nov/10/game-of-thrones-george-rr-martin-the-winds-of-winter-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」2019年4月，編劇{{le|布萊恩·考克曼|Bryan Cogman}}表示他所執筆的項目不會繼續推進<ref name="#2">{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2019/04/24/game-of-thrones-spinoff-bryan-cogman-prequel-idea-dead-not-moving-forward/ |title=Game of Thrones Producer Bryan Cogman's Spinoff Series Dead at HBO: 'I Am Done With Westeros' |website=TVLine |first=Kimberly |last=Roots |date=2019-04-24 |accessdate=2019-04-24 |archive-date=2020-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520080134/https://tvline.com/2019/04/24/game-of-thrones-spinoff-bryan-cogman-prequel-idea-dead-not-moving-forward/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；科格曼確認他的前傳不會繼續進行<ref name="#2"/>。2019年5月，馬田表示其中兩個項目仍處於劇本編寫階段，但逐漸接近邊緣<ref name="#3">{{cite web |url=https://ew.com/tv/2019/05/04/game-of-thrones-three-spin-offs-george-rr-martin/ |title=George R.R. Martin says three Game of Thrones spin-offs still in the works |website=Entertainment Weekly |first=Nick |last=Romano |date=2019-05-04 |accessdate=2019-05-05 |archive-date=2020-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302124041/https://ew.com/tv/2019/05/04/game-of-thrones-three-spin-offs-george-rr-martin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年5月，喬治·R·R·馬丁表示其他的兩個項目仍然處於撰寫劇本階段，但是距離成型「越來越近」<ref name="#3"/>。

==== 血月 ====
2018年6月8日，HBO委託由{{le|珍·古德曼|Jane Goldman}}擔任[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]及馬田擔任聯合創作人以進行《權力遊戲》前傳系列的[[電視試播|試播]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://ew.com/tv/2018/06/08/game-thrones-prequel-jane-goldman/ |title=Breaking: 'Game of Thrones' prequel pilot ordered by HBO. Full details ... |last=Hibberd |first=James |date=2018-06-08 |work=Entertainment Weekly |access-date=2018-06-08 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303164338/https://ew.com/tv/2018/06/08/game-thrones-prequel-jane-goldman/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。前傳故事發生於《英雄時代》中，那是《權力遊戲》中事件大約10,000年開始的時期<ref name="IGN 180616" />。那個時期值得注意的事件包括強大房屋的基礎、白色步行者首次降臨維斯特洛大陸的漫漫長夜，及當安達斯人從埃索斯入侵並征服了大部分維斯特洛人時，安達斯人的侵略<ref name="IGN 180616" />，馬田建議以《漫漫長夜》作為該系列的標題<ref name="#4">{{cite web |url=http://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2018/06/11/hbo-greenlights-goldman-pilot/ |title=HBO Greenlights Goldman Pilot |last=Martin |first=George R. R. |date=2018-06-11 |website=georgerrmartin.com |access-date=2018-09-02 |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616203859/http://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2018/06/11/hbo-greenlights-goldman-pilot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#4"/>。{{le|S·J·卡森|S. J. Clarkson}}宣布將執導並擔任該試播的執行製片<ref>{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/game-of-thrones-spinoffs-more-considered-hbo-naomi-watts-george-rr-martin-1202553210/ |title="Crazy" Not To Consider More 'Game Of Thrones' Spinoffs, HBO Chief Says – TCA |last=Patten |first=Dominic |date=2019-02-08 |work=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2019-02-25 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303170701/https://deadline.com/2019/02/game-of-thrones-spinoffs-more-considered-hbo-naomi-watts-george-rr-martin-1202553210/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年10月，有消息稱[[妮奥米·瓦兹|娜奧美·屈絲]]被任命為女主角，飾演「一個有魅力並隱藏著一個黑暗秘密的社交名媛」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/game-of-thrones-prequel-pilot-naomi-watts-hbo-1202977630/ |title='Game of Thrones' Prequel Casts Naomi Watts in Lead Role |first1=Justin |last1=Kroll |first2=Joe |last2=Otterson |date=2018-10-30 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=2018-10-31 |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519200237/https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/game-of-thrones-prequel-pilot-naomi-watts-hbo-1202977630/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/game-of-thrones-prequel-pilot-naomi-watts-hbo-1202977630/ |title='Game of Thrones' Prequel Casts Naomi Watts in Lead Role |first1=Justin |last1=Kroll |first2=Joe |last2=Otterson |website=Variety |date=2018-10-30 |access-date=2018-10-31 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519200237/https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/game-of-thrones-prequel-pilot-naomi-watts-hbo-1202977630/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一天之後，喬許·懷特豪斯（Josh Whitehouse）確認出演試播集男主角<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequel-josh-whitehouse-joins-naomi-watts-hbo-pilot-cast-1156799 |title='Game of Thrones' Prequel Casts One of Its Male Leads |first1=Josh |last1=Wigler |website=Hollywood Reporter |date=2018-10-31 |access-date=2018-10-31 |language=en-US |archive-date=2018-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031234116/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-prequel-josh-whitehouse-joins-naomi-watts-hbo-pilot-cast-1156799 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他確認演出該系列的常規演員包括：祖殊·懷特豪斯（Josh Whitehouse）、[[托比·瑞格波|托比·瑞格波]]、{{le|伊凡諾·傑瑞馬亞|Ivanno Jeremiah}}、[[乔基·亨莉|喬基·亨莉]]、{{le|娜歐密·阿基|Naomi Ackie}}、{{le|丹妮絲·高夫|Denise Gough}}、[[傑米·坎貝爾·鮑爾|占美·金寶·鮑華]]、{{le|席拉·亞汀|Sheila Atim}}、{{le|亞歷克·斯夏普|Alex Sharp}}、[[米兰达·理查森|美蘭達·理察]]、[[喬基·亨莉|喬基·亨莉]]、馬奎斯·羅德里格茲（Marquis Rodriguez）、{{le|約翰·西姆|John Simm}}、{{le|理查德·麥卡布|Richard McCabe}}、{{le|約翰·赫弗南|John Heffernan (actor)}}和迪克西·艾格里克斯（Dixie Egerickx）<ref name="TVLineJan2019">{{cite web |url=https://tvline.com/2019/01/08/game-of-thrones-prequel-toby-regbo-cast-hbo-pilot/ |title=Game of Thrones Prequel Adds Reign, Narnia and Humans Actors and 5 More |first=Kimberly |last=Roots |website=TVLine |date=2019-01-08 |access-date=2019-01-10 |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109205405/https://tvline.com/2019/01/08/game-of-thrones-prequel-toby-regbo-cast-hbo-pilot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-series-regulars-cast-marquis-rodriguez-john-simm-richard-mccabe-john-heffernan-dixie-egerickx-1202583636/ |title='Game Of Thrones' Prequel HBO Pilot Adds Five Series Regulars To Cast |first=Denise |last=Petski |work=Deadline Hollywood |date=2019-03-27 |accessdate=2019-03-31 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303164419/https://deadline.com/2019/03/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-series-regulars-cast-marquis-rodriguez-john-simm-richard-mccabe-john-heffernan-dixie-egerickx-1202583636/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/03/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-series-regulars-cast-marquis-rodriguez-john-simm-richard-mccabe-john-heffernan-dixie-egerickx-1202583636/ |title=‘Game Of Thrones’ Prequel HBO Pilot Adds Five Series Regulars To Cast |first=Denise |last=Petski |publisher=Deadline Hollywood |date=2019-03-27 |accessdate=2019-03-31 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303164419/https://deadline.com/2019/03/game-of-thrones-prequel-hbo-series-regulars-cast-marquis-rodriguez-john-simm-richard-mccabe-john-heffernan-dixie-egerickx-1202583636/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。劇集計劃於2019年中期在[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]]及多地開機拍攝<ref name="TVLineJan2019" /><ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/game-of-thrones-spinoffs-more-considered-hbo-naomi-watts-george-rr-martin-1202553210/ |title="Crazy" Not To Consider More 'Game Of Thrones' Spinoffs, HBO Chief Says – TCA |last=Patten |first=Dominic |date=2019-02-08 |publisher=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2019-02-25 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303170701/https://deadline.com/2019/02/game-of-thrones-spinoffs-more-considered-hbo-naomi-watts-george-rr-martin-1202553210/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年5月13日，英國《[[太陽報_(英國)|太陽報]]》稱該部前傳已在[[貝爾法斯特|貝爾法斯特]]開機拍攝。同年6月11日，馬田在一篇博客中建議用「長夜（The Long Night）」作為這部後續劇集片名，並透露試播集的拍攝地點、演員和導演仍未確定<ref>{{cite web |url=http://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2018/06/11/hbo-greenlights-goldman-pilot/ |title=HBO Greenlights Goldman Pilot |author=George R. R. Martin |website=georgerrmartin.com |date=2018-06-11 |access-date=2018-09-02 |language=en-US |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616203859/http://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2018/06/11/hbo-greenlights-goldman-pilot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後來該劇[[暫定名稱|暫定名稱]]為「血月（Bloodmoon）」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/9067339/game-of-thrones-prequel-filming-belfast-bloodmoon/|title=Game of Thrones prequel Bloodmoon has already started filming in Belfast|last=|first=|date=2019-05-13|website=The Sun|language=en-GB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515181029/https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/9067339/game-of-thrones-prequel-filming-belfast-bloodmoon/|archive-date=2019-05-15|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-05-16}}</ref>。2019年9月，馬田稱試播劇集正在進行後期製作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2019/09/16/i-could-tell-you/ |title=I Could Tell You… |first=George R.R. |last=Martin |website=georgerrmartin.com |date=2019-09-16 |accessdate=2019-09-19 |archive-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416231644/https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2019/09/16/i-could-tell-you/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，然而在2019年10月，HBO宣布決定不繼續進行古德曼的前傳系列<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-naomi-watts-led-prequel-dead-at-hbo-1250795 |title='Game of Thrones': Naomi Watts-Led Prequel Dead at HBO |date=2019-10-29 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |last1=Wigler |first1=Josh |last2=Lesley |first2=Goldberg |access-date=2019-10-29 |archive-date=2020-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520131735/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/game-thrones-naomi-watts-led-prequel-dead-at-hbo-1250795 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 龍族 ====
{{main|龍之家族 (電視劇)}}
2019年9月，《[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]》的記者內莉·安德烈耶娃（Nellie Andreeva）報導指，馬田與賴恩·康達爾（Ryan Condal）撰寫的第二部前傳「追踪著坦格利安家族的沒落開始」，這幾乎已經接近HBO的試播，由於它是基於2017年科格曼的想法，故此該項目不算是原始的第六個劇本<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/house-targaryen-prequel-game-of-thrones-series-ryan-condal-george-rr-martin-hbo-1202732221/ |title='Game Of Thrones' House Targaryen Prequel From George R.R. Martin & Ryan Condal Nears HBO Pilot Order |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |date=2019-09-12 |website=Deadline |access-date=2019-09-12 |archive-date=2020-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513171454/https://deadline.com/2019/09/house-targaryen-prequel-game-of-thrones-series-ryan-condal-george-rr-martin-hbo-1202732221/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這部名為《龍族》的前傳於2019年10月29日直接被選為系列作品。這部10集的系列劇集是建基於馬田、文斯·杰拉迪斯（Vince Gerardis）、康達爾和{{le|米格爾·薩波奇尼克|Miguel Sapochnik}}製作的《{{le|火與血|Fire and Blood (Game of Thrones)}}》的資料而製作；而後者兩人更成為該劇集的節目主理人<ref>{{cite web |last1=Patten |first1=Dominic |last2=Andreeva |first2=Nellie |title='Game Of Thrones' Prequel 'House Of The Dragon' Gets Straight To Series Order From HBO |url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/game-of-thrones-new-series-house-of-the-dragons-targaryen-hbo-max-greenlight-1202771886/ |website=Deadline |date=2019-10-29 |accessdate=2019-10-30 |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031224013/https://deadline.com/2019/10/game-of-thrones-new-series-house-of-the-dragons-targaryen-hbo-max-greenlight-1202771886/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年1月，HBO表示該系列劇集計劃於2022年推出，以及寫作過程經已展開<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |title='Game Of Thrones' Prequel 'House Of The Dragon' To Launch In 2022; HBO Boss On More 'GOT' & Pilot That Didn't Go – TCA |url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/game-of-thrones-prequel-house-of-the-dragon-premiere-date-2022-hbo-boss-more-got-pilot-naomi-watts-1202831792/ |website=Deadline |date=2020-01-15 |accessdate=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2020-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200514014621/https://deadline.com/2020/01/game-of-thrones-prequel-house-of-the-dragon-premiere-date-2022-hbo-boss-more-got-pilot-naomi-watts-1202831792/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

